title: Pawmates: The Dog Meetup App
description:
Featured on 50+ news and media channels including BlogTO, Narcity, Newsweek, CTV, City News, Global News, Curiocity, and many more

Downloaded more than 50,000 times in 20+ countries

Pawmates is your friendly neighbourhood dog meetup app! Match, chat, and meet with dogs and their owners near you!

Find your pack! Looking to meet with like minded people who love their pets like you do? Look no further! Our matching works just like your favourite meetup apps. Swipe right on pups you like, left on those you don’t. Once you’ve matched with them, you can chat freely as much as you want, for free. We do NOT believe in pay to message (who wants to do that?)

Our features include:

CREATE YOUR CUSTOM PROFILE
Post photos of your pup, add details about them including their personality, age, breed, and more!

MATCH WITH PUPS
Unlimited free browsing of the cutest dogs in your area! Change your settings to specify the types of dogs and people you want to meet! Find your gang!

CHAT AND MEET
Pawmates matches show up on your custom wheel! Swipe through your match wheel and start chatting with people and their pups!
Connect with pups near you by organizing meet ups!

OUR PET BUSINESS MAP

Looking for the top rated vets, pet food stores, walkers, or anything else related to your pup like the best park in your area? Hop on over to our Pawmates Map and check out every animal business in your area!

Pawmates is here not only to help you meet your new dogpack, but to help with every other need of pet owners and we're growing daily! We want to build the biggest community of dog lovers around the world. So come join our family today!

CONTACT US!
Have questions, problems, or feedback? Feel free to contact us @ Pawmatesapp@gmail.com Or visit us at our Instagram and Facebook pages to win amazing prizes and giveaways!

YOUR PRIVACY IS IMPORTANT TO US
Please read the terms and policies of Pawmates, as well as the privacy policy carefully. All data is handled under the terms and policies of Pawmates privacy policy. More details can be found here: https://pawmatesapp.com/terms-of-service/

Adding the option to delete chats would be good.', "12 people are within my 50 mile radius. 7 of those people want to breed their dogs. 2 of those people want to date. And another 1 just wants a pet sitter. This app isnt regulated Edit: I did attempt to report these profiles. There wasn't a report option. Or it's incredibly difficult to find. Either or.", "Won't use proper location. Locks when I try to update the location. Won't let me delete account.", 'Fantastic app loved all the people', 'Very user friendly app. A lot of great matches for my little Barky. Me and 🐕 really loving this app.', "I love pawmates but they are the same dog s and no one manage me back but it's still a good app", 'This is a great way to meet other pets. 5/5!!', 'Great app my dog loves it']

title: Boo - The World's Cutest Dog
description:
You’ve got a new pet – Boo, The World’s Cutest Dog! Play with Boo in the park and cuddle your new fuzzy friend to sleep. Take awesome selfies with Boo and upload them to your BOO-stagram!

Boo, The World’s Cutest Dog, is here, and he’s ready to hang out with you, his human! He needs lots of love and attention, and what’s more fun than loving this cute little fuzzball? Experience a day in the life of Boo – Give him a bath before it’s time to go to the vet. Dress him up in his favorite outfits. Play frisbee with him at the park and cheer him on while he’s racing against his puppy friends. Make sure he’s fed well before you tuck him into bed! 

Features:
> Dress Boo up in rockin’ outfits!
> Oh no! Boo’s not feeling well. Cure him with your special vet tools!
> Have a fun-filled day with Boo at the park!
> Boo’s hungry! Feed him yummy food to make his tail wag! 
> Ready, set go! Help Boo win the doggy race!
> Let Boo splash around in a bubble bath ‘til he’s squeaky clean!
> Play a lullaby for Boo and tuck him into his cozy bed!

To opt out of CrazyLabs sales of personal information as a California resident, please visit our Privacy Policy: https://crazylabs.com/privacy-policy/
summary: Boo, The World’s Cutest Dog, is here, and he’s ready to hang out with you!

comments: ['Amazing game! I have alot of fun playing this on my tablet. And now on my phone!! The only problems that i dont like are you have to buy stuff. Such as you have to buy bath time, unlock some items, And for bedtime, and nurse, I dont know of you can actually unlock these items if you keep playing, but i do love this game alot! I would recommend it. Very fun and entertaining, and theres a bug i found, where the fur goes threw the shirts sometimes, but other than that awsome app! I love it!! 😍👍', "This game is great overall but I have two problems the first one is that I have to pay for bath time,nurse,and I also have to pay for the things in the park and the feeding time. My second problem is that the fur goes through the clothing and I would like to have those things changed pls.but it is a great game so that's why I rate it five stars.❤️🐾🐕🐶", "I LOVE this game boo is so cute! And I love the times when he sticks his tounge out because it's so cute if you get it in a picture the race is fun it reminds me of a video game and the fashion contest is just as fun to! All this game needs is to fix the thing on Android were boos clothes are all glitched it makes me sad cuz then I can't wear them! 😭🥰😁", "Hi!!., so I have a problem with boo because when I dress him/her up her clothes glitches and some pieces appear but some don't I used to play this when I was a kid nothing was wrong but now it has some bugs please fix this Thank you so much!!! But overall this is a great game he/she is so cute.", "This game is so fun to play. He is so cute. I love this game but one thing I don't like about this game is that something's are lock like the vet etc. It's not only the problem in this game but every game that is made by coco play or tab table has this problem. Some levels are always locked. Please improve this.", 'Best game ever loved it so cute!!! 4/5 stars because I would love it if you could unlock all of the places like the shower or bedtime as such so please if you could make it easier to unlock them... 😉😉😉', "Cute adorable game but you guys are unfair or what! This is a kids game and yet you ask to pay to unlock most of the rooms like the bathroom Etc. You can't expect kids to pay money for a game! Seriously that's just wrong and takes the fun right out of it fun for them. And the parents can't always afford it either! Also there's far too many ads on the game. Unistalled!", "I love this game! It's super cute! The only problem is I can't get any of the ones that are locked. Thats the only problem. Could you fix it? Over all, good game!I would rate five if you could fix this problem. 4 four stars!", "I love this game boo is just the cutest dog ever 😍😍 👍Thumbs up for the pple who made this game. Now what I wish you could add is if we can play with other players in multiplayer and if boo can go outside the house and even play with friends online or offline. Also if u could add humans to take care of boo and also u can dress the humans. u can choose if u want to be a human girl or boy or be a Couple in the game. Lastly maybe if u can add skins and dresses.Hope it's not too much😁🙏", 'This is a good game but it is intresting to play it once only and most of the things are locked for purchasing . Please fix the purchasing with the false coins of games and do unlock more features without real money . Please fixed these things', "I love this game, their is so much to do. I love the graphics. I love adorable boo. I play for hours and i don't get bored. I also love that their are so much activities. The only two defect is that the bedroom and bathroom and doctor office are all locked ,otherwise its perfect", "I love it! It's easy to play and you can know how to take care of a pet, namely dog. The puppy is really, REALLY cute too! To unlock more stuff, you need to pay. But the game itself is free and I totally recomend it!!", "It's good because I played this game as a kid before. But there's a problem with the clothes. All of the clothes I made it wear are all glitched and that was my first time seeing it glitched. I took a screenshot of it to proof that it glitched when I first started the game. Please fix the problem.", "Boo is the most beautiful and cute and adorable when I was little I played it when I'm 8 now I played it again because it's my favorite game this game is cute for toddlers to play with it please say yes I love it soooo much and I love your games that you made and toddlers like boo the worlds cutest dog is such a beautiful game and I wish I got a dog like that and I loved all of your games that you made the end...", 'Used to be a great and fun game!!! All of the sudden though this game has more adds a bunch of glitches and now you need a pass to go to the park!!!! This game also takes up a lot of data just to "post" one picture of a dog!! Horrible game I would NOT reccomend!!!', "This really a nice game. But I give this game only 2 star. Because when I go for dress up Boo there is only 4 dress is unlocked! And all dresses is locked. And the 'Bath', 'Doctor Clinic', and 'Bed room', is already locked. And in the playground 4 item is unlocked to play and all item is locked.", "It's I really really good game. The dog is Soooo cute. My only problem is too many adds and lots of the stuff you get for the dog is locked. If you really want the whole thing you have to pay. But I do think it's a good game and you should get it!", "I think it is amazing the dog is so cute and you can even do a cute pageant but it's sad that you have to pay to get the sleep and shower etc other than that i love the game I have it on both of my electronic things!", '3 stars because almost everyone is locked and the timer for play time. Plan on updating where everything is unlocked please and where play time timer is only a few minutes or seconds!', "The clothes went into Boo's fur and I could not see the clothes. I wish that all of the rooms were free because they are needed for the dog, and I would NEVER pay $13.99 for no ad's and for the rooms it's kinda stupid. Although I love the dog, super cute.", "My new favorite game! I loveeeeee my boo and he is soooooo cute and this is now one of my new favorite mobile games! One thing I don't like is that, well, for instance, you have to pay money in real life for boo to take a shower. But you don't have to if you don't want to.", "This is very cute and all, but almost everything costs real money and they look very interesting. Please make less stuff money, like how about the doctor or bedroom? Please , I would've given it 5 stars if those 2 were for free. Also the bathroom too (optional for you creator)", "Adorable but glitchy. The fur goes over most of the clothes, so you can't really see them. Especially for the pants. You can't really see them.", "Th outfits went into their dogs skin and looked really weird if this is a bug please fix it I do not want other people to see them clothes go into their dogs skin anyways I do like the places u can go to but I wish more of these things were unlocked because I done a race and he was Hurt so I went to the doctors office and it was locked so I couldn't help him then but I do like all the stuff on there! :D", "It is a terrible game unless you are a literal 3 year old pretty boring all you can do is feed Boo and you have to pay for stuff and you can dress up there but it's boring and the graphics are cute though but it only gets two stars for me the snakey snake who is seven thank you P.S. honestly when you're dressing up boo the first kind of comes through the stuff and it looks really weird delete this game now I am ordering you goodbye", "This is a really awesome game I say that you really should get it the only thing is that something's are locked and I think you might have to pay for it it if you want to be able to play that part of the game but other than that this game is amazing I think you should get it. It is a good game for everyone one more thing there are no ads.", "This app is so much fun!!!!!!; I love to click Boo's photo and send to get likes and all,every single detail and feature is so amazing. Its better you all install this game if you are a dog lover. I m a dog lover so i intalled this game and i was just amazed to see. Its just fantastik.😊😊", "I love this game because it's so adorable and like I can dress him up and I can play with him and everything but it does contain a lot of things you have to purchase so that's the only downfall but the best part is getting to play with little boo he's so cute", "I would highly recommend this game could so fun but far I don't like about it is you only get to play at the park every 5 hours Plant part of it five hours but it's so easy to collect stuff and the dog is so cute", 'This game is very fun but it does have a few glitches when I first got into the game I wanted to dress up my pet but the clothes were glitching through its fur it did that for all of the clothes and shoes but not for the glasses but overall this game is pretty fun', "It would be better if the people who made the game would make it so now almost everything in the dress up part you would have to buy but it's really good just have to buy alot", 'Hate I had to pay for other when I grow up I will make game like this but all. Are free but I love o It just make it all free and the dresses are maybe you just buy it with money money in the games not real money and maybe make some mini games so we could get some money and buy some dresses', "Boo is sooooo cute😄 I love the Boo'stagram and everything and I love this app but its a little bit glitchin when i was in the race and please fix the glitch in the race and its easy to play too and I loved and enjoyed this game I had no problem with this except the glitch but I think this is my best game in my phone love it soooooooooooooooooooooo very much", 'I love this! But I wish everything was free. And there is also some bugs here, if you could fix it do it but overall this is a great game.', 'It is nice to play this game it is fun to play the dog in it looks so cute and the things to do are also nice and fun means that going to the park , bathing the dog, sleeping etc... I like this game.', "Very very cute, but everything's locked so it's not very fun. Don't waste you're time, unless you want to buy the full version!", 'This game is do fun and cute i love pomeranians so much', 'Dude why is this so cute? The only thing that annoys me is the voice that says, "GO!" Its almost very annoying. But the rest of the game is very very cute!', "I liked this game as the food which the dog ate looks so yummy and I was literally craving for it . Yum😋😋. Boo is so cute and I only play this game for the food ,i can't stop myself by looking at the food as the chicken is just so delicious", "I like it. I uninstalled it many times. I checked it when 2018 started 😁 Yeah sometimes its boring but I rate it 5 because it's so cute and awesome game."]

title: DogDater
description:
Few animals are as social as our dog friends, yet no social App is devoted to THEIR needs for daily quality interactions until now! DogDater is an app created by dog lovers for dog lovers to help your dog flourish and find new friends. It allows you to follow and meet other dogs around the world regardless of where they are and based on your personal preferences such as breed, characteristics, and gender. 
The App includes lots of functions that will make your and your dog’s life happier: The yard allows you to stay up to date on what your favorite dogs are doing. You can also showcase your dog's life and news about it. You can create and join groups in your area or based on your dog's interests. This is a great way to connect with more dogs and to share tips and thoughts about your and others' dogs. You can also send direct messages to other dog owners and meet up, or recommend nice dog places, exciting parks, or any favorite dog accessories your dog might want to share with their friends. The App also makes it easy for you to keep track of your dog's family history, and find your dog's long-lost brothers and sisters.
We have just launched the App and are planning to add lots of exciting functions very soon, such as a marketplace, online courses, dog psychology, dog walking, dog sitting, parking, mating, and pedigrees for breeding all over the world. Welcome to DogDater The world's best community for dogs!
summary: The App for all dog lovers. Find dogs around the world & around the corner.

I'm not gonna commute with my two dogs, one of them with arthritis, to meet another dog. I understand it might work for other people, but it is a very simple feature to add an address to the account information and be able to search based on that. You basically already have that with the city...", 'Fantastic app. Really been waiting for an app like this. Thank you for making it happen!']

title: Dating.com™: Chat, Meet People
description:
Join Dating.com™ dating app and discover one of the world’s most popular, responsive and feature-rich dating apps. Tap into an online dating community bursting with great single people, conversation and love. You’ll get an instant buzz! 
Dating.com  is the stylish dating platform that allows you to meet single women and men in over 75 countries. Grab your chance to transform how you date online and meet singles – someone really special. Whether you're seeking a relationship or simply looking to meet people and expand your social circle, our platform offers a seamless experience for everyone looking to connect. Send your life in thrilling new directions…
Get the most out of this powerful, must-have online dating app: 

🌏 EXPAND YOUR CHOICES
Dating.com lets you connect with single women and men. You have so many options to find a date in Europe, America, Australia, Asia, and beyond. Get closer whether you’re traveling or dating online from home!

💘 FIND WHATEVER YOU WANT
Match exactly with whom you want whether you wish to find a friend, or it’s a serious new relationship, exciting chat, or a mix of everything. And get an acquaintance every way you want with our ample features. Variety is the spice of Dating.com online dating app!

😍 DATE SINGLES WITH A DIFFERENCE
Dating.com online dating solution offers you an unrivalled set of features big on innovation.

💞 EVERY FEATURE YOU’LL NEED
•	Register FREE to browse and connect to one of the most popular dating apps.
•	Search for a virtual date based on your preferences.
•	View stunning profiles and high-quality photos of singles.
•	Get notifications when someone looking for friends messages you.
•	Watch live streaming of attractive singles.

✔ Subscribe and get premium features to find new friends:
•	Access private photos & videos.
•	Chat with people online in real-time to get closer.
•	Use offline messages to stay in touch and talk to new people.
•	Video Chat: meet face-to-face. 
•	Swap photos and build trust.
•	Send stickers, animated smilies.
•	Try Let’s Mingle and get more interest.

🔒 COMPLETE PEACE OF MIND
We are committed to safe dating, privacy protection and member verification. Our AI-powered screening and moderation system safeguards our community 24/7. You can depend on our online dating service! Date safely with Dating.com!

♥️ DATING.COM – DEVOTED TO YOU
Dating.com offers you the freedom and flexibility to meet new friends or match and date single people anywhere! Over 25 years of expertise and purpose-driven technology has given us the power to make love happen in new ways. Online dating inspires us whether it’s a two-way private chat or a live party stream. That’s why we match millions of members online every day. 

IMPORTANT SUBSCRIPTION DETAILS
•	Subscribe to chat with other members via this app.
•	Choose one of three great subscription packages to use premium features – 150 150 Credits/month ($29.99 for the 1st month, then $69.99/month); 400 Credits/month ($142.99); and 950 Credits/month ($269.99).
•	Your Google Play account will be charged once you confirm your purchase.
•	Your subscription will renew automatically unless you cancel within 24-hours prior to the end of your current subscription.
•	You can switch off auto-renewal by going to your Google Play account settings after the purchase.

Terms & conditions: https://www.dating.com/terms/

comments: ["This app is pretty expensive. I also found it weird that some messages seem to be auto-generated because they aren't appropriate replies. The messages did not address things that we were discussing. And one more thing, I am not keen on subscribing monthly where they auto-renew and auto-charge when you ran out of credits. My credit cards and/or debit cards should only be charged whenever I want to purchase credits. I do not want a regular subscription.", 'First, the subscription/credit is expensive. Second, it seems like the popular accounts are scams or computer-generated so you can purchase more credits. Observe the messages/mails you receive and also the pictures Third, a chat is charged one credit but the longer the message, it cost more credits. Reading an email alone costs 10 credits. Definitely not going to recommend this.', 'I this app is good for meeting new people from different parts of the world. i like how secure it is and i think it has a 90-95% matching accuracy. Its just that its too expensive for average/mass users. i think its too much for viewing photos and watching videos being sent to you.. just think about it.. sender spends some credit to send photos, videos to other user and the recepient had to also spend some credit to view those. chats are also expensive and are limited to a few characters', 'It was a nice app, I would have given it a 5 star if not for the expensive pricing of credits. the dollars spend here can equal to the amount of monthly and even for some, a yearly subscription with free messaging & replies to everyone. I know you are trying hard to give the clients the best app, however, some users are having difficulty always buying credits. I hope you can fix this issue, come up with a fixed amount of price for the monthly subscription of credits but not overpriced.', 'The app is nice. You can meet different people. But there\'s only limited credits for viewing and sending emails and chats. How i wish there\'s only a feature on the app that needs an upgrade. It\'s unfortunate for those who can\'t afford the upgrade/premium feature. If your aim on the app is for your users to meet the "right" person,then there should be no limit in sending emails or exchanging chat messages', 'This app is unbelievable. Scammers. I was using a free subscriptions for a longer time . And i just tried for the first time to purchase a credits using my paypal. And to my surprise they process an auto debit to my card. They say its auto renewal and I cannot ask for refund. Well I did not authorize that one. You just sucking money to the people. Everything is expensive. I will give you guys a zero score.', "It is a nice application but it's so expensive for me. BETTER NOT TO SUBSCRIBE if you don't have enough money. Messages are always interrupted due to consumed credits so you need to buy it in order to chat and I think it's costly for me. I no longer want to keep paying every month when the features are too limited. I already sent an email to cancel my membership and subscription cuz I'm worried that they will automatically charged every month.", "nice app. just wish it were easier (less credits) to chat with people whom you have started communicating with...especially if you don't have a lot of money to buy credits. And beware I had several scammers contact me. Always fact check and do reverse image searches because no dating site can prevent scammers. And for some reason, men in China said they could not see my pictures on my profile. ??? What's up with that? The app makes you pay to message 'popular members'.", "Worthless. You pay monthly subscription £33 plus on top of that you have to buy separately credit like 20 credit that u can send only 2 texts with it, with 20 cradits you can send 2 texts only, and that 20 credits cost £22 so you can't even have normal conversation with the person. Plus everyone is in USA I personally didn't see no 1 from UK. Such a waste of time and money", "it is not a good site asked for a membership cancellation on 10/08/23 via email as I no longer want to be a member a yet they continued to ignore my request so they can continue to take my money. They have continued to send match email notifications though. They have so called customers support on WhatsApp messenger and email but no reply from any of them. it's over priced for what it is. i advise anyone not to us this app", "It's very,very,verrrrryýyy. Expensive.. 🥴🥴🥴.... I never never never.. purchase here again... super expensive. The email you received from the person had an intention to you. You have to pay for it before you open. Before you reply. You have to pay, they have a limited credit in every purchase you want.. 🙄🙄🙄🥴🥴🥴 and there is no free credit. Even if 5 credit only a day..", "You charge me as a monthly fee , yet when you run out of credits there is no access to anything on this site til you by more credits .. I like the site seems genuine . but way to dam expensive to get any kind of good convo going with some one .. there should be at least free text messages with someone that has been in a long conversation with .. it sucks you credit packages have to big of a gap between them .. make some more smaller packages .. and don't be so dam greedy ...", "The app is great but it was soo EXPENSIVE even you meet someone that interest you, the conversation is very limited, because you have to spend big amount of money to continue the conversation and to know the person, I DON'T RECOMMENDED THIS DATING SITE, they really not helping us to find that special someone, they just take advantage of our desire to find happiness, by milking money from us. Most importantly there are lots of fake profile, it say confirm profile but fake.", "I'm wondering why this app exists if not to scam people for money. Great concept of app, which could have been great if genuine with customers at heart. All profiles seem to be fake or some form of robotic/AI generated pictures, messaging and responses. It's useless if you don't pay for the exorbitant fees. Please don't waste your hard earned money on this app. The app's representatives responding here all seem defensive and very robotic responses with no human touch.", 'This app is incredibly expensive, with every single chat and letter costing a penny. I find it strange that some of the messages appear to be repeated or automatically generated.', 'Be very careful. I talked with some nice people on this site but avoid the "popular members". None of them are interested in an engaging conversation, only how many credits you can spend. They never really read your profile and even if your profile is blank they are still full of compliments. Every single "popular" member is the same.', "help centers states if your plan isn't enough & you want to upgrade then they would help with that. They didn't even want to refer it to a manager. No response from any messages except phone, Prices are very high. Seems to me many with free account wiill encourage more exspensive communication- emails, pics. They can get %of precent value- what other incentives do they recieve. So are there to create followers", "This is the worst site I've ever been on. Day1 I was overwhelmed by 200+ (canned messages) which initially is a plus until you realize to answer you have to pay $24.99 for 1000 coins. Each response depletes 60 coins, your money is gone in 16 replies. You should notice the patterns of responses regardless the language, * Short one sentence replies *Rushed to get you to cybersex *Never willing to go to text, FB, IG Don't waste your money, most likely paid people to keep you on the hook.", 'Everyone on this app is not real. Employees put fake profiles, and the fake people send you presents and videos, so you will buy credits to talk to them. I was scammed by several African scammed posing with fake pictures. Whatapp and Signal Communications were fake. The people I communicated with used the same questions and answers. They used the same romantic jargon.', "Everything is for paying subscribers . In the free version you can't send messages or email. So unless you're willing to pay for a subscription this app is not getting anyone a date. Useless app.", 'This app is a big scam..i search all the photos of a popular member who message me and i found out that their actually using other people pics from instagram,be careful dont talked to them and take not do not suncribed its too expensive and many of the user are fake so dont waste your time in this app..', "This app costs so much, if you have no money you can't connect to anyone and even if you pay for subscription you are only limited to your credits. This sucks.", "Please guys don't ever purchase here coins or even monthly cause this apps is really scam.i purchase for 1month 1,500 only a few msg i send then i need to paid again also the men there i really think and im sure they just pretending also but still they just want to make money from you.specially Philippines girl don't believe this apps they are just wanted your money.its very big lier guy there they will ask photo and then you paid a lot of coins...", "I don't think the people are real!!I just opened the app after registering and received messages from two girls immediately...!!!It doesn't Make any sense!!!", 'Obviously, the popular members are dummy accounts used by agents to lure you in spending more money in buying expensive credit points. In addition, I just recently loaded 20credits and I just checked on the email, it went down immediately to 5.', "Very Costly and secondly thing is even after having great chat with the girl/bot,they still say we haven't talked much.Finally I came up with an idea to share my number and email addresses so that we can chat outside the app but seems like they just want you to chat here to lose your coins on this app due to their ex is still following her so they can't trust anyone outside this app blah blah...and tons of excuses.I realised these people are prostitutes.Fraud app,just playing with our emotions.", 'This is scam, you must rename this into "Pay to Date" , or "Pay to meet" , everyone!!! this is not for meeting purpose but to income purpose you can read and send few message, but the succeding have price to pay.', "I'm quite sure this app is a scam ... It’s very expensive, and the people on here all look like models with professional photography and videos. The messages seem likebtheyvare all from bots. Please do not waste your money", 'Most of the "profiles" are simply bots, that\'s ridiculous. You spend a lot of money talking to them to find out its a big scam. Very sad the company feeds on people\'s loneliness. I\'ve tried to delete my account multiple times over the span of at least 6 weeks- nothing is happening, no response from customer service and the WhatsApp number given is none existent.But they keep taking money from my account every month, tho I have been using the app for a couple of days only before trying to delete!', "Sick and tired of mindless swiping and superficial connections? This might be the dating platform you're looking for. If you're ready to ditch the casual flings and dive headfirst into a meaningful relationship, it may be worth signing up. This app really helps me to find a mature men.", "Fake app. The men pictures look like models, and the conversations are too well thought out, plus it's TOO expensive. Trash!! Also, it won't let me delete my account.", 'Its too expensive that amount to pay just to send and receive messages it absurd. You need to make it free at least for users to enjoy it, even if you want to monitize it, it should be reasonable pls. Someone will lose lots of matches not cool', "I have read all other people's review, honestly there are 2 issues..exorbitant fees, and no exchange of contacts details.Why? In your view after how long must partners exchange contacts. Is it a deliberate way to delete contact details so that you keep members on your dating side to keep paying. Very dissapointed. Sadly it does not look like you plan to help the customers. Loneliness is indeed a crime. At least add free button to indicate you like the other person but you lack credits to respond", "Awfull. First time to use the app and upgraded my account for a month of 23€ . I thought that upgrade will give me the freedom to chat and use the app But got shook with other fees for credits deducted again from my account for 113€. I can't take it. I've emailed and i hope for a reply asap", 'Awful. All matches are coming from off shore for which I have no interest. There should be a setting for this. Additionally, the alleged Customer Service number is not available. And most profiles look like a hoax. And, the app wants money at every turn. Awful!!!!! I want to close my account... Now!!!', 'Worst app. Waste of money. Why I need to pay again and again whenever the credits get over. It would be better if you charge monthly and not for the credits.', "the video chat is not good you waste your credits and very expensive they charge by the minute and your credits go quick this site is expensive for credits and you have to wait months to get a better deal whoever designed this site is laughing all the way to the bank you are not going to meet any body here when you get to that point never happens they hide behind there phone or computer the mask is who they are I wouldn't bother spending your money you will not get a relationship these women", "For you to chat you have to subscribe. And the prices are way too expensive. You can only send one msg n you can't even read the reply from the other person. It's a scam", 'If you pay for a membership, you still need to pay to chat and read emails with credits. Too costly and some people are not real.', 'the app is very good but the subscription amount is just to much and if you subscribe for a month it takes only a few minutes chat and you will be told the subscription has finished']

title: Dog Hotel Tycoon
description:
Become a dog hotel tycoon, and create a world for your dog guests to enjoy!

CREATE A WORLD FOR YOUR DOG GUESTS TO ENJOY!
Start with a small dog hotel in a suburban area, and improve it to become the first 5+ star dog hotel! Create areas for your dogs to take naps, eat delicious snacks, play with each other, swim, excercise and much more! Anything to ensure the satisfaction of your dog guests!

WELCOME DOGS FROM ALL AROUND THE WORLD!
Become a dog hotel tycoon and accept more breeds as you grow your hotel, such as Corgi, Dachshund, Pug, Samoyed, Poodle, German Shepherd, Labrador, French Bulldog, English Bulldog, Basset Hound, Chiuahua, Chow Chow, Beagles, Shiba Inu, and many more. Each and every single dog will have their own unique character, behavior, wants and needs; and it is up to you to satisfy them!

TAKE YOUR DOGS TO DAILY DOG EVENTS!
Each day, you'll be able to take your dogs to the daily Dog Show, which is a physical obstacle challenge that will test the health & fitness of your dogs! 
There will also be a new Dog Quiz waiting for you each day, which will test your knowledge about dogs as well as teaching you interesting facts about them!

FEATURES
★ Easy to play game for every animal lover!
★ Cute Dogs with unique characteristics and lifelike behavior!
★ More than 80 dogs to have as guests, and more to come!
★ Fun rooms and items for your dogs to enjoy!
★ Send your dogs to Dog Shows!
★ Learn about dogs and earn rewards with the daily Dog Quiz!

If you love dogs, and incremental idle clicker games, you will love idle Dog Hotel Tycoon. As with all idle clicker games, you will never run out of things to do!

This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any issues with the game or have any feedback, you can always reach us at support@filgames.com
summary: Become a dog hotel tycoon, and create a world for your dog guests to enjoy!

title: Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D
description:
Welcome to an amazing life of our furry friend with Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D. Immerse in a dog life simulator, you can see the world through your dog's eyes. You will interact with hundreds of naughty and difficult challenges and have fun with all the perks and pitfalls.

You have to choose the right family. Being a good dog or a naughty dog depends on your decision. Think carefully before making a choice. Make up your mind! Try Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D for FREE now. 

🐶 How to play Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D:
- Choose and create your favorite dog.
- You are free to make choices that affect the outcome of your dog’s life.
- Care for your dog and make him happy.

🐶 Game Features:
- A variety of challenges and opportunities for your dog to explore.
- Smooth and addictive gameplay.
- Awesome 3D graphic.

Don't miss this awesome game for all pet lovers. Download Dog Life: Pet Simulator 3D, start your dog life journey now, and see how your dog's stories unfold.
summary: Observe world from dog's eyes in dog life simulator & make the right choices.

title: #Dating - Online dating app
description: Welcome to Hashtag Dating (aka #Dating), where you have the freedom to date your way. Over one million people have already joined. Match, chat, flirt and connect with local singles in California, Texas, New York and more! ARE YOU READY TO CHANGE THE RULES? Gone are the days of pointlessly swiping through boring profiles and meeting up with people you have nothing in common with. On #Dating, hashtags immediately reveal shared interests and desires so you can easily meet new people online, make friends or even fall in love. Transform the way you explore your interests and have fun! HOW IT WORKS ❤️ Add unique hashtags to your profile to show potential matches what you’re interested in ❤️ Hashtags reveal shared desires, so you can find and be found by like-minded people ❤️ Swipe to the right if you like what you see. If they like you back, you'll match with each other! ❤️ Match, chat, flirt and have fun online with people who like what you like Interested in a long-term relationship with someone who loves concerts? Searching for friendship with somebody who’s into exercise? Or maybe you just want to find people in your area? Whatever you’re looking for, download Hashtag Dating today to change the rules of the game, explore your interests and have fun with exciting singles in your area! DATING POSITIVITY Unlike many other apps on the market, Hashtag Dating inspires feel-good, genuine connections, celebrates diversity and empowers people all over the world to be their true selves. We believe you deserve to explore your preferences and make them a reality, whether you’re looking for friends or long-term love. SAFETY, RESPECT & TRUST Your safety is our top priority. Hashtag Dating is a safe space for you to explore your interests and desires. In addition to our guidelines, we've also included several safety features to ensure that you can have the best dating experience. ✔ Our guidelines are in place to ensure everyone can enjoy #Dating ✔ Notice a profile where something doesn't seem quite right? Simply use our flagging system to let us know More than one million amazing people have joined our community and are waiting to find someone just like you. Sound good? Then install the free dating app now! Follow us on social media to stay in the loop: Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/hashtagdating Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hashtagdatingofficial For more information, read our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use: Privacy Policy: https://m.locanto.com/m/dol/privacy/ Terms of Use: https://m.locanto.com/m/dol/terms/ Brought to you by the developers of Locanto (Yalwa).
summary: Use hashtags to reveal shared interests & match with exciting people near you!

comments: ['Paid $20 for the "see your likes" thing and now theres no way to cancel it. It says go to your profile and " my subscriptions" but there is no such place on my profile nor is there a phone number or email to cancel it.', 'Very disappionted Second time ive tried this app,its getting worse Have seen same profile from 2 different countries,what is going on,also shows i have liked people that i havent Get initial response for a few chats then nothing Also informs me of likes but they never appear on likes page Have complained but problem still exists Hey guys stick with free stuff go thru pay wall and get less Only 1 star and i think that is generous', "Fake and pay to do most features. The main reason why I uninstalled was I was doing something else on my phone and a message popped up saying that 21 people liked my profile and I could pay to unlock to see who they were. I'm not Robert Downey Jr. I'm not that good looking. So I know those were all fake", "You guys spamming me in my emails was so annoying that I uninstalled it. Searched for the unsubscribe option at footer and there was none however I went back into the app and I deleted it. Its an okay app but it just didn't work out for me.", "I rate it 3 Star, #1 you run out of swipes fast , #2 you have a lot of the girls be trying to get money 💰 which I blocked them. then There's a lot of trans genders to. I blocked them as well.", "Worst app!! Purchase the premium package And couldn't even use the subscription!!!", 'Im trying to cancel "see who viewed you" but there is nothing to click on to cancel is this just a way to scam people or what?', "Yeah now I'm getting repeated people that were matched not even ten seconds ago and I'm certain that there are more people from the USA that uses this app but I'm mostly getting overseas. Seriously this has gotten worse. Not only that but I've had these same issues before and it looked initially that they were fixed. They aren't fixed at all.", 'girls just send number but do not chat.. seems spam or marketing technique', "Indians beware of the profiles on this app. Most of the matches found on this app are nothing but scammers. Never reply to people who send their contact info beforehand also never ever contact their number. It's a scam and you can be trapped. They might ask for certain demands for free but never do that. Apart from that app is good no issues. Needs a verification system for face, email, photo, email, location and number it's a must. Developer should add this feature to their app.", "Disgraceful there is no a option to select a country you need to put all countries around the world, for example I live in Greece but I can't find it 30% you put about Africa or South America and about Europe only French and German or Spanish, thank you for this, this is a waste of time fix your app with the location immediately. I unistalled it, also why don't you do the algorithm about enable location, like other dating apps. I will install it until you fix this issue.", "I cant message any of my matches, it keeps saying invalid email. I've tried changing emails and contacted support but have not received a solution. Fix your app. Edit: I have sent a few emails. Have not received a solution. Edit#2: They asked me to make a new account but I already have 10 matches on this account.", "App is easy to use and avoids the pay wall bs. However when someone likes you, you have no way to view that person or even get a hint of who it is. Would be nice if that feature was implemented. Edit. They added the like feature however it's hidden behind a pay wall.", "There is no verification in place. All females images taken from Instagram with a strong emphasis on the upper female body parts. The communication I've had is all bots/scammers. Virtually every user is well over 1,000 miles away being shown on repeat. Avoid this one, my guy.", "paid $35 for a subscription, yet that doesn't unlock everything... only unlocked the who liked you page... for unlimited likes, it's another $40 subscription. Not at all worth it, and kinda want my money back!", 'In rebuttal to the apps developers response," it is quite apperent that the developers have seeded this app with pictures and profiles of other users in different states," as well as using pictures of porn stars.. all without there consent!" strictly to fleece there consumers into useage! While collecting information about every aspect of how you as the consumer, navigate through there app, using state of the art algorithms! Basically mining your information to be sold to the highest bidder.', "it's not working properly", "I am on this application from last 2,3 months but still I'm not getting messages from other users. I am getting notifications for matching but none of them has received my message. I think most off the users has left the app. Please provide me proper solution for this issue.", "Looks real nice, has a fair amount of features, and works alright, but could you please please please add the hashtags #vegan and #vegetarian ? There's not a lot of places to find these folks, and I rather match with someone in that realm. It's a big deal. And why no descriptions? Not super bothered by the lack, no problem if that's what you are going for to stand out, but I guess it would make your app better. Handy to see someone's own choice of words and discern their personality before chat", "This app shows you the same fake pictures over time so it looks like more women are using the app. Real women don't post pics with low cut outfits or in their underwear but a lot do here. Pics of the wrong gender are reported and will appear again. Locations are wrong as you will see some close and they are located in another city, state, country after you make contact. Sucks as bad as their classified site as 99% are probably overseas scammers as they clearly do not speak English.", "it's a very cool, fast and good site to find your partner", 'Usual "dating" site being overrun with spammers.', "The app isn't opening on my phone at all. It's been more than a month and it just shows network issues. I've used the app for two months before and it worked just fine. Please fix this.", 'Well if I have the app for Locanto USA why does it also send me hashtag dating are they the same app', 'Beautiful app 👍 I recommend everyone to use this app as I got many friends globally. I used paid version. There is some disadvantages, I could not see any Russian profiles or any other which I need. Secondly the app is freezed , now I need to open the app 3 times to respond to any new messages I receive. I really want them to provide us a upgrade for the app in order to remove the bugs or errors. 5/5 app, thank you.', "GPS distance not working set to 50 miles getting matches over 10,000 Miles away in the opposite hemisphere it is impossible to find a local when you're in Canada and it's recommending people in India, Mexico and Philippines. Since I live in multiple locations in 2 countries I would like to be able to post and search where I am and where I usually am as well as where I'm going to be.", "By far I'm not enjoying this app and people have started leaving because they're message doesn't seem to go through I've sent numerous messages and yet no reply and out of frustration most users with the same issues are leaving the app I tried messaging customer service through Facebook and never got a reply which is very bad nobody seems to get a reply back", "On the surface, this does work and maybe it isn't a scam like most dating apps on the play store. However there aren't any real profiles. Just obvious fakes that a three year old can point out. Not worth the space on a phone, much less paying money for.", "So app ain't bad but communication in the chat is weird, as if the app doesn't send the messages, only gripe so far but hope they fix it! I'm in a conversation atm and waiting for a reply but the msg probably hasn't bn sent. It's been 4days.", "Though it's a good platform, Opposite gender profiles are shown, just not one or two, at times 20 + profiles are shown. Please avoid OTHER GENDER PROFILES.", "I'm trying to cancel my subscription and I have tried to cancel it on every place they have been telling me and I still can't find anything. I don't know anything about it because it was my first time trying online dating. I am starting to think that they're making it hard for you to cancel it so they can keep it renewed !!!", "After a reviews of this app, intend to try this app but i have just wasted my time 😠 The registration has been stuck in between while uploading pictures.... Tried several times 😔 Very annoying 😠 Omg..!! You make me add my mail id, phone number, & photo still not able to process 😡 It's a waste of time 😡😡😡😡😡😡😡 Worst app ever... Better to remove after waited couple of hours 😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡 I wish I could give you - star", "it's good, stress reliever 🤗", "it's a nose app just that I have not understand everything on it", "Very poor Dating App. I rejoined this Dating App. It is so quiet, dead and boring. Nobody are willing to match with me. Don't download this App, it is a waste of time!!!! I uninstalled after not hearing from anyone and could not change my profile's photo.", "Totally a useless dating app. Don't create an account here... Absolutely no point installing it. It's so quiet. title: Fetchadate
description:
FetchaDate is Where Pet Lovers Meet! The place to connect for friends, pet playdates, and especially a date for you!

DATING, FRIENDS, PET PLAYDATES
What we do at FetchaDate is eliminate the hurdle to who you’re looking for. We are the dating app where singles meet over what they already love: dogs, cats, and maybe even exotic pets.

Those who trust FetchaDate are people who treat their pets as family so you don’t have to worry about them not being a “pet person”. Now, we can’t guarantee every person on here loves animals, but chances are they wouldn’t be here if they didn’t.

NO PET, NO PROBLEM
We understand people may be between pets at the moment so ‘No Pet, No Problem!’ Choose from a variety of virtual pets that represent your lifestyle like a bird, fish, turtle, horse, pig, or even a snake!

HERE’S HOW IT WORKS - YOU GET A WINGPET!
You can tell a lot about a person through their pet and that helps make better matches. With FetchaDate, your “WingPet” starts things off making your introduction. Your pet’s picture is seen first, and your pet gives clues about your interests. Why is the pet seen first? We feel this leads to more success, because who wouldn’t swipe right on a cute pet? And, Fetchadate creates a better experience by bonding over common ground.

CHANGING THE RULES TO FIND YOUR MATCH
Searching offers a few options:

1. See a pet you like and swipe right. And, if their owner swipes right on you, find them in your “Matches” tab. Swiped right but not a match yet? They will appear in your “fav’d” tab.
OR
2. See a pet and scroll up to get clues about the owner before swiping left or right.
OR
3. Need to see the person before swiping? Tap on the ? to see who’s behind that pet and select a heart for yes or X to keep fetching.

PROFILES: FETCH - MATCH - DATE
In FetchaDate, it’s quick to create your free profile including your values, interests, and personality. A profile also consists of name, age, location, occupation, and motto. And, you get to make a profile for your real or virtual pet.

FREE TO USE PLUS UPGRADES
FetchaDate is free to download, and create a profile with a limit on swipes, and chat!
We offer optional in-app purchases of monthly, 6 months, and 1 year subscriptions with discounts available. Subscriptions offer boosts, extended swiping, chat, and additional pet profiles. Price chart is displayed in the app before making a purchase.

Any free trial period is for a limited time. Any unused portion of a free trial period is forfeited after purchasing a subscription.

Payment will be charged to your Google Play account after purchase confirmation. Your subscription will automatically renew for the same term and price. You may cancel your subscription up to 24 hours before the next billing cycle.

You can manage your subscription in your phone’s account settings.
If you don’t choose to purchase a subscription, you may continue fetching on FetchaDate for free with limitations.

FOUNDER
Sheryl Matthys is the bestselling author of Leashes and Lovers: What Your Dog Can Teach You About Love, Life, and Happiness. From the moment Sheryl got her first Greyhound, people on the streets of NYC started talking to her. Right then she knew the secret to dating, friendships, and love! Sheryl’s appeared on ABC World News, Animal Planet, BRAVO, E!, Fox & Friends, The New York Times and more.

TERMS AND PRIVACY
Fetch on FetchaDate worry free. Check out our terms and privacy policy.
Terms of Use: https://fetchadate.com/terms/
Privacy Policy: https://fetchadate.com/privacy-policy

comments: ['Not enough users. I set my radius for around 30 miles, got one profile that I was not interested in, then no one else. Expanded my radius to around 50 miles, got one profile I accidentally swiped left on, then profiles have shown up since.', "Cool App! I love dogs and animals! If you're looking for someone, this would be a good place to find someone with similar interests.", 'This is a cute, easy to use app. I would definitely be using it if I were single, will refer my son to it.', "Great app...great idea....even linked up from Australia.....and it's inclusive of my three mates, my two staffies and my lorikeet", '"Unexpected error occurred" EVERY time I enter my phone number to open the app...🤨👎', "Doesn't work, after I type in my phone number press next. It will not complete the action.", "Can't even open app. Keeps shutting down.", "I thought this would be Great idea because I love dogs and would love to meet someone with the same passion, but it's not accepting my phone number. It doesn't let me go any further. Anyone that can help me?", 'I like the concept. But what about other pets besides Dogs and Cats? What about Birds and Reptiles lovers?', 'It is a very easy and useful app to use', "It's and interesting take on dating but truth is if my dog don't like ya I won't either", 'Pretty cute concept', 'Not many close options in Ct', "It doesn't work", 'Finally an app for me.', '𝓕𝓮𝓽𝓬𝓱𝓪𝓭𝓪𝓽𝓪 𝓘𝓼 𝓣𝓱𝓮 𝓑', 'Seems cool', 'Wow wow', 'Gg']

title: Dog translator
description:
Get the dog's attention and listen to the dog's voice. Intelligent human-dog communicator. It integrates various animal sound simulations such as dog and cat communication, dog language and cat language translation, etc. It is a tool for teasing pets, which is convenient and worry-free.

Long press to record human voice: Input what you want to say to your dog, it will be converted into dog language immediately, the dog can understand what you want to say, and feel your full love for it!
summary: A tool for teasing pets, which is convenient and worry-free.
developerAddress: 广东省佛山市顺德区招商·依云国际-4座2609

title: OkCupid: Date and Find Love
description: Get the best online dating app experience and match-up based on who you really are and what you love. OkCupid is all about inclusive online dating for every single person! The dating app that lets you experience real adult dating for those who know what they want! With OkCupid, you can meet new friends online or find serious relationships, date and make meaningful connections. Find your match and a date for tonight! This matchmaking app cares about you. We’ve created an exciting online dating environment for every single person. Try it now and start your journey towards better relationships. Personalize your dating profile with your interests, what your dating expectations are, and leave the rest to the matching algorithm! Great Romantic dates come from true matches - that’s why the OkCupid online dating app shows off who you are beyond a photo. Meet cute singles, build connections and find love! You deserve it all! • Love is inclusive, and so is OkCupid. Create a free dating profile that highlights what makes you special and unique. • Find your soulmate from over 60 different gender identities and sexual orientations: Gay, Lesbian, Bisexual, pansexual, queer and more. Gay marriage can be more than just a dream. • She/her, he/him, they/them - highlight your gender pronouns and meet locals near you! • On OkCupid you can find everything you are looking for - Asian dating, Afroromance, Gay hookups, Latino, straight, or anything in between - love and connections that transcend borders. • Go on great dates, and find your match by giving your own unique answers! • Round it off with your cutest profile picture and you’re ready to meet new people, find love or go on a great date tonight. • Meaningful connections can come in many shapes and sizes - create new friendships, chat with new and interesting people, find a new exciting romance, or a serious relationship! OkCupid isn’t just another online app for dates. Our free dating app helps you meet singles, connect, chat or have a deep conversation through our one-of-a-kind messaging system. Focus on the connections you’re interested in without the ones you’re not. Then, plan to meet up and go on great dates - whether you’re looking for local dating, virtual dating or anything in between! Take the stress out of online dating. OkCupid can help you find your match, whether you want casual dating, marriage, or just to find your love story – YOU choose what matters. Match with people with similar interests and receive a personalized match percentage when you answer our unique questions. We’re here to help you find relationships on your terms. Flirt, find love, build connections and go on great dates with OkCupid, the best free dating app! Download now! MATCH, CONNECT AND MEETUP • Meet new people and find relationships with our unique messaging system • Local dating features help you meet people nearby DATING APP UPGRADE OkCupid is a free dating app for everyone, but we offer an optional premium subscription that unlocks exclusive features. Additional premium dating features include: • See who likes you without having to like them first • Send unlimited likes for more date matches! • Set Dealbreakers so you can find just who you're looking for and match on what matters Meet singles and find great connections – download OkCupid and enjoy the best online dating app today!
summary: The only dating app with a matching algorithm! Meet cute singles & find love!

comments: ["I like the concept. I can see if I would match with a person based from their answers on the questions if they answered a lot of questions. what I don't like is almost everything is paywalled. if they make it cheaper and regional priced, then sure. i find it expensive to pay for every features when they can just bundle those features so you pay one time. a user end up paying more. And I tried all the premium features. They're not worth it. those people who liked you are people you swiped left.", 'Well, the last update removed the "nearby" filter while swiping. The app already completely ignores your filters, you will never see or be seen by anyone within 100 miles. Been using okc on and off for almost a decade, it\'s really fallen off. The questions are the only unique selling point, and no one fills out more than a handful. Using this app is just swiping left on the same people every day, regardless of whatever dealbreakers you set. At least messaging is still free, bet that won\'t last.', "The search function on this app JUST SIMPLY DOESN'T WORK, making it aggravating to try and use. You can select 50 miles and the app will still show you someone well over 100 miles away. The passport feature, allows you to search for women in other countries unless you plan on traveling to that country this feature is useless, and theirs no way to disable it.", 'This app is poorly created and tested. When I look at the message list, it doesn\'t show me the last messages with my connections. It just shows " It\'s a match" which is absurd. I would like to see the last message without actually clicking on the connection to read the history of the conversation. This happens after few days of you and your connection talking over the app, roughly 2-3 days later. It works fine for the first couple of days.', "Ridiculous! I remember when this app was less than $20/mo. To ask for almost $50 now, is ridiculous. Pros are search parameters, which are some of the best options around; less profiles seem fake. Cons are that the experience is no where near the price you pay. As with most dating apps, you'll magically receive matches all throughout the period you're not a subscriber, but when you're finally able to see them, they're totally outside your set preferences. Those preferences should apply to all", "Currently one of the better dating apps I think. Texting is a little slow if you write multiple messages. It stops and erases what you're typing. I'm also getting the same match notification like 15 times. And it sends you notifications that someone likes you when you're out of swipes for the day, that's a little annoying. Otherwise, plenty of people and plenty of matches!", 'Decided to try the a month of the subscription to see all the matches that had piled up, 99% were from across the world and had almost no profile. My preferences will reset randomly and show me "recommended" matches outside of my search parameters (age difference, gender, location, etc). Sending a like let\'s you send an "intro" to stand out - but super likes don\'t? You can still see the profiles of the people you\'ve liked, but not the ones you\'ve super liked or sent intros to. Save your $$', 'Months ago I paid for a subscription which is supposed to allow you to see all of your intros at once. It does if you use it in the browser, but if you use the app it says "upgrade to A list to see all of your intros" which isn\'t even the name they use for their subscription anymore! I contacted support, was never given any sort of resolution, & cancelled my subscription. I signed up again yesterday & the app is still doing the same thing - no fix for this ongoing, documented issue. Total SCAM!', 'Still won\'t load past 20 of my "You Liked", and is only partially showing "Matches". Swiping is clunkier than last update. Can no longer see the intros I wrote to people I haven\'t matched with yet (I think it used to be in the "You Liked" section or my Messages). I can\'t find my Matched in my messages anymore if I leave the screen before the "You Matched!" popup finishes loading (which used to be ok!!). I matched with someone and sent a message, but I can\'t find it anywhere after!', "This is one of the few dating apps that actually functions correctly, and has actual humans on it. There seems to be a few fake profiles, or at least some really old ones that haven't been touched in years (people still wearing masks and talking about the China flu). Overall, it's ok, and you can match and chat with people without paying. It can be buggy at times, and the app seems to struggle with distance limitations, but it does do what it claims.", "First off I really love how customizable your profile is. I really enjoy being able to answer so many questions and getting to see how much you match a potential partner. That's a great idea and no other apps do this. However the base app gives you criminally low swipes before you have to wait to swipe again. I paid for the basic ($34) for unlimited swipes and I don't feel like it was worth it tbh :/ I have 47 likes and can't match with a single person :/", 'instead of a "your turn" category in the messages, just make a panel of every one who has messaged me and make it stay there even if i replied again and they haven\'t yet. also add a search bar to find people better. i have more than a hundred matches and the messages categories are really inconvenient. not happy about it. it would also be very useful to be able to select multiple people to unmatch instead of doing it all one by one.', "I paid for a subscription, and all was fine, but for the last couple of weeks before it expired, I had no likes and no matches of any kind. It ran out yesterday and overnight. I have 13 likes and lots and lots of matches. Obviously, it's a way to try to get me to resubscribe, but what a con restricting access to matches and likes towards the end of a subscription. Bear this in mind if you use this service.", "Recently come back after a long lay off. It's exactly the same. Except now it just recycles all the matches you've left swiped on. I must have seen the same people now about 300 times each. - anything that's a deal breaker you have to pay, setting preferences doesn't work at all and still shows you matches nowere near you. You can swipe for free but everyone, and unsuitable matches and even in other countries are shown. I have a ton of likes and obviously you have to pay to see them. Scam.", "The people are awesome and I like the option to answer questions and see other people's answers, but the app is loaded with bugs. At one point half of the likes I got and my conversations were deleted and the support couldn't do anything about it. From time to time the app stops working and I can't login. Now all the text I wrote in my profile got corrupted and the support can't restore what I had there. These issues happened mostly recently, so I hope they'll start fixing them soon.", "For some reason, the app refuses to show people in my distance preference. I live in a rather large population area, but regardless, I'm only shown people over 25 miles away when my preference is 10 miles. I refuse to go a whole state away just to have one date. Fix this problem.", "I tried this in its heyday,; interesting method of a social networking system by a series of interest and questionnaire. But I tried logging today, even post update seconds ago. I couldn't, tried the web version. Denied too. I guess not only could I not delete my account but even after the latest update, this app has officially been turn redundant that logging in is not possible. Farewell and onwards to hopefully better ones.", 'Don\'t pay their subscription. No matter how broad your settings, there will be users who selected you but that you cannot see. They will keep spamming you with the same profiles over and over no matter how many times you\'ve swipped left. Do not waste your money on their subscription. They also hide their top picks "cupid\'s pick" behind additional payrolls even if you are already a paid subscriber, while feeding the same profiles over and over. Do not pay for the premium subscription!', "The worst dating app. I don't know if this is true, but I'm guessing the vast majority of profiles are very very old. No way to verify new vs old profiles. I have had pretty good success on every other main stream dating app but not Ok Cupid. I did get tons of likes from people on other continents however.. totally useless and prob the most expensive of all dating apps. If I could give it Zero stars I would. Garbage.", "Wow this App doesn't work in a million different ways. I subscribed and paid the six month fee, and the app started to malfunction! All my matches and conversations either never saved or would disappear. Any messages I would reply to would not post to the match and then my filters didn't work! I was getting feeds of people outside my choices even though I had deal breakers I contacted support and fortunately they gave me a refund. It still doesn't work...What's the point if the APP doesnt work!?", "Won't let me cancel premium. Ended up getting billed for a month I didn't want, and it is set to bill me again for next month. So the link to disable your subscription in the app doesn't go anywhere. It's decoration that tricks you into thinking you canceled. You have to log in on an actual web browser to cancel a subscription.", "The main advantage of OkCupid over its competitors is its matching questionnaire/algorithm. But, the questionnaire page has a horrible interface. In the web version at least, when you re-answer a match question, the screen then takes you back the top, forcing you to scroll all the way back down again, re-loading the questions that are too far down. It ought to be divided into multiple pages instead of set up as an infinite scroll. You also can't skip questions that you had previously answered.", 'I paid. But the features were not worth it. It was still impossible to change the preferences. After the subscription ended - exactly the next day, I received 10 likes (while only 2-3 during the whole 3 months). It is up to you if you think it is real or fake likes...', "Something's terribly wrong with this app. Notifications don't work no matter what I set in the app or in my phone's settings, the Likes and Messages sometimes have a dot in them despite having no new content, Boosts get actived by themselves (cache issue?) some of the profiles text is gibberish and events always feel delayed, wether it's the animation lagging or the backend. It's like the app is drunk; either that or the developers.", "Absolute worst. It has just been a day since I installed, created an account, and paid for the subscription. I was using the app when I got logged out unexpectedly. Now, I can no longer access my account using my mobile number or my email address. Wth. And yes, I tried reinstalling the app. It didn't work.", "I just signed up 10 mins ago. It said success and then was shown a sign in page. It would not let me sign in. I tried installing the app on my phone. Tried again. It told me my account was banned. I have no idea why. I'm just a normal person using photos and info I've used on 2 other dating apps. Tried contacting support. I can't. It's requiring me to sign in to speak to support. That's the problem. I can't sign in. Maybe someone there will read this and help me. :/", 'There are pros and cons to this app. Unfortunately, in my experience there were more cons than pros. Pros: I like the questionnaire & the commonalities percentage meter. Cons: Needing a subscription to see likes. Most likes were from foreign countries on the other side of the world. After paying for a subscription, the app went radio silent. OK Cupid ran out of recommendations for me and suggested looking at profiles in other countries. In my opinion, save your money and try a different app.', 'Probably the best app there is for what it does. Where other dating apps requires insane kinds of cash for just about anything, this one actually allows you to look for people, and send them an intro message, without it costing anything. If your intro, or match, is returned, texting them costs nothing. However, there is a massive amount of mainly Asian/South American/African location faking going on - You might set range to 50km, which apparently includes several continents <- Only gotten worse.', 'Worst so-called dating app. Very low quality profiles. And same profiles keep rotating. 70% of profiles have no pics. Even if you set preferences, the app disregards those and keeps showing you profiles outside your preferences; because number of profiles are very limited. You will not get a single decent person to talk to. Just waste of time. Uninstalled after trying it out for a month.', "The best of the dating apps, in my opinion. Tons of users, tons of swipes, able to send a comment with every like, able to like specific parts of the person's profile, able to change location, able to look around in the global pool, all for free. You can also really customise your profile.", "I like the idea and concepts. But technically it works so bad, matches don't appear on the list. I encountered multiple bugs and when reached to customer support they treated me like an idiot and dismissed my problems. I repeat. The app is super buggy and doesn't work correctly", "This app is loaded with bugs and it's gotten worse over time! The same people keep coming up even though I swipe left on them everytime, even the blocked ones! Intros on 99% of the profiles are gibberish and not legible. People with a 90% match have complete opposite answers to mine... And how are there so many profiles without pics of the people's faces? I uploaded a pic once that didn't show my face and I was emailed numerous times warning me that it would be taken down! Not a good app at all", "What a scam, 44 new likes, pay $100 to see who they are....sucker! They're all from other countries even when I select nearby. What a grimey app. I want a damn refund...NOW! You app isn't allowing me to cancel subscription to premium. I select cancel and it glitches or does nothing. This isn't surprising, you've found a way to trap subscribers into being locked into a system where nobody can be contacted to cancel payments. I will he speaking with my lawyer.", 'Deceptive advertising when you uses their app several times and are charged $45, then they can\'t find your app. No refund because you used their service. They should advertise "x" communications cost $45, rather than make you think you have unlimited access. This is the definition of DECEPTION ADVERTISING. I have gotten a dozen from letters that claim they are working on it. Support is worthless. They tell me I am using the wrong email, which is why they can\'t find my account.', "Another app with no customer service what so ever. Just automated responses. I've emailed them 3 times saying I can't login or reset my password and they email me a link to reset my password.... I really hate technology sometimes. The app also has this weird bug when I'm writing in any of the bio sections it just scrolls all the way down and I can't see what I'm writing.... The price for a month of the premium service is absurd.", "The pricing of premium has wildly increased over the last 4 years. The cost of one month is now what 6 months cost 4 years ago. 6 months roughly works out 162% increase in price nearly triple what it was 4 years ago, which could be an indication of the app collapsing, some of the matches aren't even real profiles anymore, it has fallen far from where it was", "Recommends individuals far outside set preferences, from age, distance, and smoking preferences Allows spam bots from foreign countries to fill up likes Continuously keeps pushing ppl you pass on, unless they like you, then you'll never see them show up in your feed again Could be a great app, but they'd rather add more gimics to get $$$ from people.", 'Hello, Recently I noticed that my new matches do not appear in my list of matches which gives me no possibility to message them. They simply disappear right after the pink screen saying "it\'s a match". I have updated the application but the problem is still there. Can you please correct this as it makes the app completely useless as I am not able to speak to new people. It\'s a shame because otherwise I really enjoyed using this app, when it was working...', 'Better site now you can message/intro without matching again, and Profile and Photo verification now added though few do it. Still too many fake profiles and catfish that unfortunately fill up the site and waste time. Too many profiles also reappear again and again, even if you swipe left! Being able to share photos in messages would be better too, then you would know the petson is real.', 'I don\'t normally review apps, but this one was so bad, I had to say something. I\'ve been off and on this particular dating app for 4 years(give it take), the only "real" interactions I\'ve had fizzled quick. But lately, I\'ve been seeing the same profiles I\'ve already swiped on. Right or left, doesn\'t seem to matter, but why would I pay for a broken app? And based on others reviews, the paid version isn\'t any better. Talking to random strangers will get you more matches than this app ever will.']

title: Dog Evolution: Idle Merge Game
description:
If you’re a dog person and think you know everything about man’s best friend, your world is about to be rocked! Mix puppy breeds like you’ve never seen before and discover a whole new canine dimension that will leave you barking in such awe: the possibilities are much wow!

Dachshunds, beagles, corgies and retrievers are so last week. Evolved dogs should have an extra eye or two so they can watch over their human friends more efficiently, or a handy horn just in case they get into the odd bar skirmish with a mutant unicorn. It’s your duty to let the dogs out and help them evolve!

DOGE FEATURES
• Pantheon: a new place for supreme beings to look down on us mortals and laugh at our misery
• Impostors: watch out for impostors trying to steal the spotlight from the puppies

HOW TO PLAY
• Drag and drop similar puppies to create new mysterious doges
• Use dog eggs to earn coins, buy new creatures and make even more money
• Alternatively, fiercely tap a rabbit to make coins pop from their eggs

HIGHLIGHTS
• Different stages and many dog species to discover
• A mind-blowing story with surprising twists
• The unexpected mix of creature evolution dynamics and incremental clicker games
• Doodle-like illustrations
• Various possible endings: find your destiny
• No dogs were harmed in the making of this game, only developers

The dog days have just begun! Much fun such wow!

Please note! This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. Some features and extras mentioned in the description may also have to be purchased for real money.
summary: Combine mutant dog breeds and find out just how wacky puppies can get!
