comments: ['Pretty fun, just a bit repetitive but I love it', "I enjoy the app it's cute and it's nice to pass the time, but it's kind of difficult to play a game and genuinely enjoy it when it crashes every single time you play an ad unwillingly. I'll just be in the middle of tapping my dogs and then an ad will play and crash the entire app so I have to reopen it every single time an ad plays Please fix this problem", "I love this game!!!!! its so addicting! who ever is reading this,you should get the game. I've been playing for hours. And it is helpful when your on the go or having no wifi,you cam still play the amazing app!!!! I never really got any ads. the only time i had a ad is when i tried getting more diamond diamonds.", "It's really fun and addicting. I could play for hours and hours, maybe even days. The genius who made this game blows my mind. I can't wait to download more games like this fantastic one. I only have had this game for a little, but I already 💗 it! When I am playing it on my phone even my dog sits and looks at the screen. I 💗 playing this game in a frantic time like this. I can't have a minute were I'm not playing, thinking about it, or talking about it! This game makes me feel 🤪😋😍. I 💗 it!", "It's a good time waster that's ruined by way to many ads that pop up freely on their own when you're just changing a tab in game. I wouldn't be so hard on it if it were just to watch the ads when you want to and get double payout or some type of reward.", 'Love it This game keeps me going and is very relaxing. But, when you get higher in the game, you have to watch an ad whenever you click on Mars. I like the app, but not the ads.', "I've always loved these games. They're my favorite evolution games. The only reason I'm not giving it 5 stars is because I ran into a bug that affected my gameplay. I contacted Tapps, but they have not responded. I hope no one runs into this bug too...", 'it literally shows you an ap every half minute. this is ridiculous', "Fabulous game, very addicting, adorable dogs and I'm definitely going to get into trouble for playing it too much when I'm not supposed to >:)", 'I redownloaded this game after over a decade just for the nostalgia. I will tell you now that this game did not disappoint. I still love this game, it is so cute and easy', 'I have played these games on and off for years and i love them! Funny, weird, cute and casual gaming, from getting far in the other evolution games i know it gets even weirder so i cant wait to see all the doggos. Very easy to learn.', 'Amazing! Its such an entertaining game and there are so many different types of dogs! There is a reasonable amount of ads and there is also lots of ways to make the process faster. I totally recommend it, it is a fun and simple game.', 'It\'s a good way to kill time, but I hate the new "evolution boxes" takes you out of gameplay and if I\'m just trying to tap, I cant do that anymore :(', "TO ALL THE PEOPLE WHO GAVE THIS A ONE STAR FOR THE ADS: There is a very free and simple trick to avoid these. TURN OFF YOUR WIFI. Ads can't get through without wifi to transfer it to your screen, so next time you think about complaining about the ads, remember: TURN OFF YOUR GOD DAMN WIFI", "Interesting time waster, but there are so many ads it ruins it. I can't even find the option to purchase the game just to turn off the excessive ads.", "This game is cool but... It has a LOT of ads. Its like they don't care adout there people who play their games. But it fun so if you don't care about ads play this game.", 'So fun! Lots of cute things to do and the doggos are great. All the little details in all of these games are great! (I have 5 from the same company thing)', "Ok think it's a good game but you need to make the poops cost more ,the diamonds easier to get and the cost of power ups cost less.", 'I have bad wifi so idk why ppl are complaining about the freaking adds i only saw 5-6 adds :/ but its simple, and cute, the designs, are, auhh, i like it but the designs, i dont like it.', "Literally everytime I try and open the app it crashes💔 I'm not sure if it's because of my device, but it's really sad😭 it's despair induuuuciiiingg- I've played it before though so it is a good game! I pray to Atua it will start working👉👈", "The game is good but there are too many ads so I can't able to play the game properly so fix that issue.", 'Its a really fun and cool app to play. At the super market , the school bus , any where is fun to play', '100000/10 I had been grinding this game for a few years when I had my fire tablet and only had one dog and 2 alien dogs left until my brother smashed the tablet. Very enjoyable tho and I recommend to anyone <3', "You might find the ads annoying but don't worry! You can turn off your WiFi, you can play it offline and online!", "It's very fun and it helps waste time. The graphics are good and its super adorable 😊", "Game is nice, but too many cheap ads just keep popping up like every minute - they're ruining the experience.", "*its just an evolution game about dogs.* *that's it.* Yet it's so creative compared to other evolution games. So I give it a 10 out of 10.", 'Very fun, especially when waiting for someone or on a flight or when you need to pass time.', 'I love these games, they are just so much fun to play when ever I am waiting for anything from the end of my break to the bus.', "Ads always show up and it's annoying but I appreciate it when they give coins after watching ads :D", "Great app if you're bored, and inspirational characters. I even drew some of them. 💛", 'I really liked this game, its really fun! Yes there are ads here and there either way its amazing! I really recommend this game! -this is my dad acc and im 12', 'THIS GAME HAS WAY TOO MANY POP UP ADS! Every minute or so.... The game will give you an ad, I say never get the game.', "pretty fun, kind of time consuming, gets boring after a while, but it's still fun", "It's a cute little time waster, but 3 ads in 1 minute is way too excessive.", "Very nice. Very nice. I loike it. Because it's very nice.", "It's SO FUN and the dogs are adorable❤ this game is so addicting and I find myself playing it all day. I highly recommend it❤", "I'm a dog person so I love this game and thanks for the update", 'This is is great, funny, and cute game I have no complaints please dont change anything about this game it is great', 'Great and awesome game 👍 graphics are really clear great quality and controls Awesome make more of these please!']

title: Old Friends Dog Game
description:
Welcome to Old Friends Dog Game, where love never grows old! Create your own dog sanctuary in this heartwarming pet rescue simulator. Rescue adorable senior dogs and uncover their life story as you shower them with love. Decorate with cute doggy decor, bake scrumptious dog snacks, and experience the joy of helping cute senior dogs live out their golden years in the best way possible. 

Inspired by the real life pet residents at Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary, these cute dogs have heartwarming stories and personalities that you'll uncover as you rescue them and provide the care they need to live their best dog life!

Awarded Gold winner at the 2022 NYX Awards, a finalist for Pocket Gamer's Game of the Year, and a Webby honoree for Social Impact in Games, this cute dog simulator is a must-play!

Gameplay:

❤️ Meet the town residents and rescue cute senior dogs. Help them live their best life by fulfilling their needs and ensuring their happiness. As you feed, pet, and play with your dogs, their love and loyalty grows.

📘 Choose how the story unfolds. In this dog simulator, you pick the path for each dog's story! Unlock multiple chapters for every cute doggy you rescue.

💒 Customize your dog sanctuary and make it a haven for your dogs. Decorate indoors and outdoors with cute doggy decor that will make your dogs feel right at home!

🧁 Bake lip-smacking treats for your beloved dogs, ensuring they never go hungry.

🧣 Dress up your dogs in cute pet outfits! Each dog has adorable accessories that you can earn.

🐕 Give your dog sanctuary the personal touch - feature a custom profile, a unique avatar, and a gallery of cute photos of each dog!

**********

Old Friends Dog Game is developed and published by Runaway.

This game is free to play but does contain some items available to purchase for real money. If you run into any issues while playing or you have any suggestions, please reach out to us at support@runaway.zendesk.com. OLD FRIENDS DOG SANCTUARY™ is made by Runaway Play.
summary: Save cute dogs and help them enjoy life in this pet rescue simulator!

comments: ["I love this game! The art style and the dynamics of the game is beautiful and calming. Despite of being somewhat new at first, the game only needed a few tweaks but it was already enjoyable. I'm really glad they included events in the game~ it's engaging and addicting 🖤 (I'm planning on editing this review from time to time if I see/think of something to comment about!) • as others have mentioned, there are rarely 💩 dropped in the sanctuary.", "Absolutely loving the game so far! I'm relieved it's not another match 3 or merge 2 games, and really is about taking care of old dogs and managing the sanctuary. I've seen the game's advert for a long time, I regret not playing it sooner. But better now than never I guess! Only thing is the game keeps crashing on me occasionally while loading a new scene (ex; getting a new dog, loading livestream, .etc) I love the game and I want to support the funding, I'd appreciate a smoother experience. :')", "I played the game a while ago and recently reinstalled it, but now it won't even let me past level one. Everytime I try to stream it just makes the screen go black, and nothing happens. I've tried everything to fix it, reinstalling again, restarting my phone, even went online to try and find an answer. Love the game, just wish I could get further with it.", "I absolutely love this game! It's adorable, and I haven't experienced any bugs (I have played for about a month now). Though, for the Dog Blog, there are limited color options, which, as someone with bright green hair, is a little saddening :( Aside from my dramatics about hair color, I recommend everyone give this game a try! It's so customized, and each dog has their own favorite treats and toys, which is so fun to memorize. I love this game!!", "This game is really amazing and I love the style so much! I really like the game because it's supporting a real life senior dog sanctuary too! But last 3 or 4 days I couldn't get in the game because i got a message about some kind of error and I tried everything to get rid of it but it hasn't been working so far. I got pretty good progress there so it's going to be sad if i lose it. I don't know if its a game error or its like that for someone too but I hope it gets fixed soon!", "Very Cute very relaxing it's really wholesome too! But, I've been having issues lately When I stream the screen becomes black and the music keeps playing and I can't go to the next level because my first time of streaming is glitching I've been having Issues with that so whatever you could do please Fix it....", "First things first, this is not a game you will play for an hour straight. More like a few minutes at a time. Gameplay is fun though. Little thing I mentioned pre-edit, So basically my progress reset, (It has been fixed now.) Devs should probably look into what caused that. Also I don't know if the message I sent to tell them it was fixed worked? All in all, great game, great devs. (What caused the game to reset though?)", "A awesome friendly game where you get to experience adventures and journey with these adorable dogs and the amazing artwork! I love this game. It's just heartwarming. And there is so much more potential to expand apon! The fact that it was based on real dogs and experiences is also amazing. You get to read snippets of real-world inspiration the further you progress.", "This is THE BEST chill/idle kind of game I've ever played. There's so much to do! You are always getting rewards constantly, even past the early game. There are only ads very rarely, when you want to increase your rewards. The dogs are so sweet and have personality that you uncover through their individual story lines. You'll fall in love. I had this game ages ago and left it like I always do with mobile games (I'm fickle lol) and this is the ONLY game I missed so much I had to come back again!", "This game is fun but I got stuck on the streaming stage Everytime I tried the screen would go black to the point I just left and rejoin the game and when I kept trying it took my stuff but never worked if u could see if it's a bug please update Soo it doesn't happen to other people", "it was almost an amazing game, except for the fact that it was lacking in furniture and decoration aspects. it's fun caring for the dogs, but i wish i could put more furnitures. there's so many furniture blueprints, but i cant craft becuz the materials for good furnitures are so hard to get. i wish we could buy materials from donations, or we could get from streams. idk. im quite unsatisfied witht the reward rn", "This make me cry so much. I love idle games. I love that this is based off an actual doggy sanctuary with the actual doggies and with pictures of the actual doggies attached. I'm sad and happy and my heart melt. Some lags and bugs are experienced and the game crashes too. But i just love the concept of this game. Good strategy to make ppl adopt senior dogs and cry cause they're gone too soon", "It's really great especially for dog lovers! I Love it a lot and especially that it's also a real sanctuary.. It really makes me wanna donate now :( but my parents do not allow me sadly... I hope some people will still donate :) definitely will recommend some friends to play this..!", "Old friends dog adventure is such a fun game where you care for older dogs and play the challenges! You get to choose what to say and there's even a dog blog! Definitely would recommend.", 'Sancuaty names could be more customizable(wanted to name mine after my old pup, Timber.) But otherwise, The game is amazing. The graphics are great. The dogs are adorable. And I love the hat for Mack.', 'Absolutely what I was looking for in a game, perfect with little to no ads and with very reasonable microtransactions! Would recommend', "Very cute! I would love if the game would emphasize the importance of identifying dog-friendly costumes that won't bother dogs vs coatumes that will make them uncomfortable all day, but overall its super fun 👍", "THIS GAME IS THE ACTUAL BEST! BAGEL IS SO CUTE MACK IS SO CUTE AND LEO IS SO CUTE,there's so many things to do!Decorate your sanctuary,collect new dogs,and it's all so much fun I love the theme and design of the game and how they're based on real life senior dogs!I wish I could meet them in real life!I was quite sad when I found out they only sold the merchandise in USD cuz I'm from the UK but seriously if I could I'd give this game a million bigillion stars out of a million biggilion stars!☆", "I am only on 3rd level, and I think it is really fun, cute, and great for a dog lover. I do find it a bit repetitive, but that will probably change over time. I olso do think Runaway's other games are really good too. If you delete their games, your progress will not be saved, though.", 'This game is so cute and entertaining! The dogs are adorable. Even the situations where almost nothing is going on it is really fun. Just baking food or cleaning the house just makes you feel happy and calm. I love this game and I really recommend this game for all dog lovers! ❤️', "It's such a cute game about dogs and don't love a dog for its age love it forever no matter what because old dogs are cute too and in the game you can unlock cute dogs like mack and bagel and Leo there so adorable doesn't matter how old a dog is love lasts for eternity I love Leo Babs and Captain Ron too runaway pls update maybe fix the bugs? Not asking for much ty the bug is it takes a bit to load and sometimes when I try saving a picture it says contact support game kicks me out any way to fix", 'I feel good playing with old friends, . I recently had to start a new game over because old friends got accidentally erased , I was devastated. Old friends helps me cope with losing my old friend scrappy. He was my everything, he passed away not long ago he was 16 and so loved. Thank you old friends for reaching out and I was very excited to hear from you. Thank you old friends.', 'This Is such a heartwarming game, I love how simple are the interactions with the dogs. I love the little stories that they include of the dogs adapting to their new home. Amazing game!', 'This game is just so adorable, and the fact that it is based on real life dogs just makes it 10 times more interesting and unique! Love it, keep up the great work. ( I also totally recommend!)', 'This game is adorable and I love the concept of it. It is so cute and so fun, and i love that the dogs each have the personalities of the real pups. And favorite treats and toys. Babs is my favorite pupbso far hehe Ten stars from me!', 'Ohh, they have fixed the problem, the game is really wonderful, and very innovative, please I recommend you download it and give it a try', "So far, it's a really fun game! However I wish furniture was cheaper and there were more coupon codes. But overall, it's really good!", 'I love this game but my account got restarted and when i just wanted to play i was in the start again i dont know to get my stuff and my progress back please help i dont wanna start again.I still have the furniture that is needed coupons. But the ones i crafted is gone and the progress of the dogs are gone and i only have mack again', 'Edit: After 2 years of playing this game, it has become quite dull. The events are all repeats from the years prior... I already have all the rewards from the bake-offs, so why even participate? I have been at the max level for probably a year now. Not much to do after completing the stories. I have 3 senior rescues myself (2 dogs and 1 cat), so this game is perfect for me. I recently applied to vet school and want to focus on old animals. This game is everything I want out of life!!!', 'One of the first times a mobile game has truly felt like a game. Love oozes from every millimeter of this experience. Even the ads are non-intrusive, and from what I understand completely optional. Highly recommend!', 'Game has reset on me twice, erasing all my progress. The first time I used recover to get back to my original game. The second time it reset, I tried to recover my original game, but only the two previous reset games appear, making me start with zero progress. If this is not fixed, I will never play this again.', "Super cute and makes me feel better about playing mind-numbing games that get me nowhere. The only complaint I have is that the app randomly restarts sometimes after an ad video. Also, videos have been unavailable for me all day so I can't get Mack his chicken flavoring 🥹", "Love the premise behind the game and was enjoying playing it. The dog message requests bugged out with no images and did nothing when I clicked on them so I rebooted the game and it lost all my data :( I'm scared it will happen again.", 'This game is so much fun, and although you have to work very hard, the dogs are soo cute. Most relaxing game ever!', "It is amazing there's lots of adventures the dogs are so cute but the best thing is getting more of the dog's stories.", "This is a cute game and I enjoy it but I can't progress past the streaming part as the screen just goes black.", 'So far this is super cute and fun. a little bit slow, but really heartwarming and relaxing.', "Cute little game. I haven't closed it since download because I'm mildly afraid of missing things when my attention differs, but that's the only issue and isn't even really one! The whole app is so fun and adorable that I can't keep my hands off of it 🙈", "I don't know why it's taken me so many years to download a wholesome game about dogs. So far into the game, it's easy to follow, lovely story and beautiful graphics. If you love dogs and want causal gameplay, this should suit you:)", "Love this game; it's so nice and wholesome! There has been issues with my progress resetting, but whenever that happens I breeze through the intro sequence then contact support through the game's settings, and they fix it in like a day. One thing I really wish the game had though is the ability to replay cutscenes, because the stories are just really cute."]

title: Dog Sled Saga
description:
A game by Dan + Lisa

As a rookie musher, foster a dogsledding team whose skills will grow if they're treated right. Week by week, get to know your dogs' unique traits, and carve your story into the trails of the Mount St. Something region.

Dog Sled Saga has a pick-up-and-play dogsled racing. Each dog's speed is hindered by hunger. Lob a limited supply of food to them to keep at full speed. Hazards on the track await.

By the time you reach the top league, you’ll need to:
- Budget monthly league expenses
- Hire and fire dogs
- Leverage fame to earn sponsorship deals
- Bring on employees for multitasking
- Breed puppies
and more.

Features:
- Pick-up-and-play racing
- Deep team management simulation
- Unique dogs with varying attributes and conditions
- True pixel-grid art style with frame-by-frame animation
- Multi-platform save sync via Drive
summary: Foster a dogsledding team whose skills grow if they're treated right.

comments: ['This game is the best! The graphics are so cute, and gameplay it\'s super fun! However I have two bugs to report. 1. When I go to type (change dog name, etc.) The game freezes. 2. Sometimes, the graphics overlap, so when I\'m in the "Journal" menu, the date and activity icons at the bottom overlap the bottom and make it difficult to read. These are minor problems, so 5 stars :D', "Loved this game when it came out but never got to finish. Came back to it, and sadly the lack of updates have made performance pretty bad. On my Note 10+ in fifteen minutes of gameplay, it froze once and had many, many issues with touch screen responsiveness. :( Hopefully the devs come back to it one day, because the gameplay was always really fun, but it's been three years since the last update, so I guess I shouldn't hold my breath.", "8/10 Really good game, would recommend. Only one problem: When I try to type something in (like a dog's name), the game freezes and has to be restarted. So I can only stick to the randomly generated options. I would hope to see this fixed, but overall it doesn't take much from the experience.", "Great game, I love the dogs, the breeding mechanics, and the story. My singular issue: the game definitely needs some optimization for mobile. Races that require 4+ dogs or have weather events like snow quickly lag, resulting in bad timing and subsequently losing races you shouldn't have a problem in. Even after I ran my phone in developer mode and forced higher processing power, the races still lag. My suggestion: get the game off Steam and play on your laptop. It's well worth it.", "Really fun game! Easy to understand, fun, and nice to look at. You can't pick your own names for the dogs without the game crashing. You can still use the name randomiser and change the harness colour, so it's still pretty good. Also the sound can't be disabled for during races, it's still really loud.", 'I love it but recently ive been getting a bunch of bugs from it, its been lagging alot and just today ive had to restart the app five times because it kept freezing. Its an amazing game and i love playing it nonetheless. The bugs include not registering my touch, clicking multiple times when ive only touched the screen once (a dog got accidentally hired because of this lol), then when i tried to add a sponsor it glitched or something cause it only showed a blue bar where sponsors usually are.', "I've played this game a couple times over the years. The art is super cute and well done. I do feel like the game could use more depth and fun updates. But for what it is it's a cute simple game. I enjoy it, but do get bored with it quickly. The races are very monotonous, I just wish there was more to the game.", "the game gets 5 stars, the port to mobile is what I'm reviewing. playing on a galaxy s9 and its glitchy on the display, the extra length of the s9 screen means there are two bars on the sides that show the background of my phone - very distracting. another glitch is when naming dogs it simply freezes up and you have to restart, so I have a few dogs with some pretty silly random names. a few times in the kennel screen, I have trouble petting or clicking on my dogs. fixes on the way I hope! <3", "This is a very cute game and I absolutely adore the pixel style and that there's a nice selection of dogs to choose for your team. The story is very interesting and I like it. It's a game I always come back to play. The are a few bugs, like the game freezing when I'm selecting dogs or try to change names, on a rare occasion, the game will crash as soon as I launch the app, but that doesn't keep me from trying to play such a nice game. I definitely recommend this game to all my friends.", 'I love this game! Its like it was designed specifically for me lol. Lovely design, fun theme, easy to figure out how to play yet hard enough to keep it interesting. One small glitch is that it crashes when I try to rename the dogs. But overall I just love that this game exists! Long live sled dogs and pixel art :)', "Still has some bugs, Can't type without a freeze and it won't save properly. I tried saving and starting up again and it just brought me back to the very begining. Besides that, I love this game. Hope it gets fixed soon!", 'This game is really fun! I love the dogs and discovering their personalities, but I do have a major problem with the game. For example, yesterday I played the game for about 15 mins, I had the perfect puppy about to join my team and I was preparing to join League 6. Then today I open the app and NONE of the progress I had made yesterday was saved.', 'This is a game I love on Steam and am excited to play on Mobile... Except for the constant freezes and crashes when trying to type. I literally cannot type anything without the game freezing and crashing.', 'I actually found this game after seeing the movie \'The Call Of The Wild\' and dog sledding fascinated me. I couldn\'t find a single game featuring dog sledding that was actually a "decent" game. This game does cost real world money but after that everything in the game is absolutely free! It\'s adorable and I love the old school pixel graphics. The dogs are cute as ever and I love the concept of them all having their own personalities and preferred positions. 5 stars for sure!! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐', "I love this game so much! I've been playing it on my computer for SO long but I really wanted to be able to play it on the go so I finally bought it on my phone. And it's still thrilling to me! The gameplay is easy and the art style/graphics are adorable! However, I wish there was more dogs to choose from. And the naming thing doesn't work but that doesn't bother me too much because I can still play the game. :) I hope this gets to the creator of the game because I would really love to see some new updates! Please and thank you in advance if you choose to update the game! :) P.S. I would really love to see a Pitbull in this game. (its my favorite breed. x3) Again, please and thank you. :) Have a wonderful day! :)", "Had a lot of fun on my old devise but now on my phone when ever I try to change anything's name the game freezes the music keeps going but the only thing I can do is turn off and back on my phone then close the app so I can play again. It's getting annoying. Please fix this big problem.", 'I love this game, it\'s what every game developer on the Play Store should take notes on as being a great example of enjoyable and the "best bang for your bark ( heh heh no sorry)". It\'s a pixel retro game with a relaxing tone with a twist, introducing the soothing music and the ambience of nature. It really engages you for a mobile game as you have to work to advance through several tiers, enough said. MUST TRY!', "I seen the game, loved it. Played tutorial, loved it. Can't name my dogs or name saves, or else the game freezes. That sucks. I'll still play it, but it sucks that I can't name anything.", 'My game kept crashing when i tried to load it on my device. The game is nice and all, but i really wish u could get a refund after what ive just experienced. The naming system ESPECIALLY needs work thought the harnesses do work so I dont understand. Fair warning fir those about to buy this game, it may be better on PC.', 'I just needed to send in feedback. Love the game from videos but every time I try to change a dogs name, the game freezes. It lets me use the "random" option, but I can\'t type a nee name', 'This game is great! I love playing this on car trips. It had no add and you can play it offline! The only downside is that you have to pay for it. But that pays for no ads which is definitely worth it. I recommend this game!', "See I love this game but it's in serious need of an update. More story, better races, it just feels like its leading nowhere. Maybe we encounter the famous dog or actually beat out rival more than a couple of times. The lack of update is why it's 3 star.", "I really enjoy this game, but I do have one or two tid bits of problems with it. 1. I can't name my dogs without freezing up. 2. I wish there were more breeds of dogs and possibly mutts when you cross breed the dogs? patterns would be cool too.", "It's an amazing game, I like that you get to customize your dogs but there is a huge flaw that sucks and I hope will get fixed soon. The naming bug. Whenever I try to name my dogs, it freezes and I have to shut off my phone just to restart the app.", "I absolutely love the game! The only fault I have with it is that sometimes when I'm racing, once I run out of treats the stations where you refill on treats wont work for me? I hope that made sense, but I'm just a little confused...", "Whenever I try too change a dog's name my game will freeze and the only way to unfreeze it is to close and reopen the app. Other than that it is a good game.", "Very very glitchy. Some days I cant pet my dogs. I cant rename anything as whenever I go to type something the game promptly crashes. Very annoying. Fix the issue and I'd give 4 maybe 5 stars lol", 'The only thing I request of this game is maybe a few more dog species and a little more character customization. What I mean by species is that you can send a female dog out and she might come back with wolf hybrids that can look like any type of wolf, such as the canis lupus, grey wolf, and the timber wolf.', "I love the art style of this game and the fact that you get your own dog sled team. BUT I'm giving this game a 3 star do to the fact that I wish they added new dog breeds like a GreatDane, Beagel, or a ChowChow for example, OR when you breed 2 dogs like a White Husky and a German Shepherd you get a White German Shepherd and not one or the other. What I love most about this game is getting new dogs but once I got all the dogs the game just kinda got boring.", 'This is a really good game except the fact that the game freezes when ever I try to type in an ame for a dog,but it will let me use the random option though.', "Dog Sled Saga is the best! The graphics are so cute, and it's so easy to learn. Breeding for certain stats is entertaining. Will definitely recommend.", "I can't write a specific name for a dog or my whole screen freezes I can only choose random names can you maybe fix that if you can? Thank you other then that it's great!", 'I think dog sled saga is a very fun and adorable game it has good graphics and easy to control. Manly there are no adds which makes me really happy. Thanks for making this game.', 'loved the game and it would have been 5 stars but when i breed my dogs and had to name the pup it wont allow me. so now the game is unplayable. pls fix this.', 'Really great game! For the first bit it is really fun game play, and adding to the story is fun, but this game needs an update. After a certain point it is just the same thing over and over again.', 'Do NOT breed two puppies at once I did and now my game is stuck on the "name this puppy" screen and I can\'t do anything about that. Ive restarted my phone, exited the app and re entered it, I REALLY don\'t want to uninstall it but I might have to 😞 other than that the game is great ^-^ but....can I get some help please? 😂', "Every time I try to change my dog's name, my app crashes and I'm forced to restart my phone as my phone won't get out of landscape mode. Ridiculous.", "Touch controls don't work in app. Unable to pass the opening splash screen. Waste of money if app is broken.", "I love this game very much. I've had it on my computer. My only complaint now is the game won't even load at all its just the blue screen and it won't load", 'I have played this game for about 3 years now and it will not let me rename my dogs or saves. I love the game and would give it 5 star if this gets fixed']

title: Dog Cafe Tycoon
description:
Our new Tycoon game! The main character of this title is our eternal friend... Dogs!

Dog staff: Dog staff manage a variety of drink ingredients! They're kind, smart, lovely, and sometimes... playful!
🐕 Milk-loving friendly Labrador Retrievers - Bailey
🐶 Smart German Shepherd - Max
🐶 Playful Beagle - Willy
🐶 Brave Rottweiler - Diesel (You don't have to worry about stealing from the cafe😉)
Get more than 30 unique dog employees!
(Tell us your favorite dog and name it! We are interested in your opinion.)

Making drinks (Cafe operation): aromatic cafe lattes, sweet caramel macchiatoes, colorful unicorn frappe!
Serve quality drinks to dog guests who visit your cafe!
The drink on the first day of the cafe is simple. It's just coffee.☕
But the next day, I make caramel frappe latte!
Will the dog customers like the drink? The daily sales of the cafe tell the satisfaction of the dog customers!
Simulation to produce a variety of drinks day by day!

❓❓ How do you manage a cafe with dogs? ❓❓
🃏 Collect various Dog manager cards.
🍹 Make a variety of signature drinks daily.
💰 Sell your drinks to customers!
🐕 Competent managers help you.
☕ You can decorate the cafe with gold earned by selling drinks.

It is the most 🐶friendly dog🐶 cafe in the world.
You can enjoy this cafe offline.
summary: It's the friendliest Dogs game you've ever met!

Gangnam-gu,
Seoul,

comments: ["The ads don't bother me, the thing that I'm struggling with is it's way too hard to get the station's automated. Especially when you upgrade them you have then have enough cards to upgrade the dogs so that it can stay automated. Seems like I'm being punished for upgrading. Need to work on that balance, but I love the art and the ideas. But way bad balance issues. Feels like they want you to pay to play.", 'It\'s fun, but it needs some improvement. Most "error" messages are still in an asian language, not translated, so I do not know what they mean. The difficulty curve also suddenly becomes very high so you\'re just sitting there waiting a very long time to continue to the next level from level 6 or so on. Everything before that was a good pace. Also, way too many ads. Feels like it\'s ads for doing ANYTHING.', "It's cute, not glitchy, not laggy, however.. There is an air balloon that floats by and offers money in exchange for a video. That thing gets in my way so often it's aggravating. Not to mention it's really difficult to get sections to be automated because you don't ever get the chance to get more managers or the money to upgrade them. So in my opinion it's a well made game with a faulty system. It quickly becomes boring when you can't afford anything.", "The style and design is adorable and the ads don't bother me too much, it's what happens after the ads. The game freezes and stays that way for about 10 seconds and some times it stays that way and I have to exit the game and get back in. I rely on the rewards from ads but since the game doesn't work afterwards I'll skip the ads and the game", 'The game would be fine without a few things. Its monetization is absolutely horrid and does the #1 thing to piss me off. When turning in "quests" you can choose a bonus for watching an ad, or not; however, should you not you\'ll still occasionally get saddled with an ad that will take at least 5-10 seconds away. Then youll also get hit with another each time you "prestige". The actual economy itself is also built around either watching ads or microtransactions to progress. I cant fit the rest in.', "Wanted to like it due to art style, but ads are far too common and intrusive. First you force me to watch one for 15 secs, but I close that only for it to then load and play ANOTHER playable ad. Close that, nope I'm forced into ANOTHER damn ad screen. All for just 1 single damn box or to advance to the next day. Ads completely ruin it for me, so unfortunately it's just not that playable for me. If it was even tweaked a little bit, it could be decent.", 'This game has a cute concept, executed... not well. The UI feels very cluttered, with 5 different "limited offer" icons on screen that you can spend $5-10 to get in game items as well as an event icon, and a float-by "watch an ad" bubble that can\'t be dismissed that cruises by every minute. You get about three minutes of gameplay before hitting an ad, most of which are short but not all. Would be super cute, but awkward pacing and blatant money-hawking spoiled it for me.', "Absolutely adorable, however I HIGHLY suggest you play I airplane mode, or have a good add blocker, the game forces you to either watch adds regularly, or spend $30 USD on VIP pass which supposedly gets rid of the adds, I'd be willing to spend money on a game, but not that much. if adds don't bother you then maybe a random hot air balloon every few minutes blocking your ability to proceed briefly will? if none of that bothers you then I think you will like this game", "The game play is standard for a tycoon game but what makes it frustrating is early on, you run out of biscuits fast that are needed to upgrade your dogs. This makes it frustrating as you have quests requiring you use them but no consistent way of gaining them. Other tycoon games are a lot better about this and it's enough where I'm at a spot of just wanting to delete the game and play another.", "Since day 1 the bonus box that you can get by watching an ad hasn't worked! It just says no ads and I have unlimited data! No excuse for it not working and so frustrating when some of the missions request that you watch an ad and it doesn't work. Uninstalling it right now. More headache than it's worth.", "I would give this 5 stars because I love this game. I love it so much I have probably spent way too much money in it. But I have 1 big issue, and that's being stuck on day 24 for over 4 months. I finally got 1 quest done in hopes it'd boost me a bit more and I only got 3 more quests done. The quests are ridiculously hard for this Day to the point where I have to wait multiple days to even level a section up. And even then, it's not enough. It's ok to make days harder as they go but not this hard", "Don't let it's aesthetic fool you. This is a game that is so desperate for you to spend money it's willing to make the gameplay worse at every point until you do. I really wanted to like it but it's actually so much more viciously designed to frustrate than most other similar games that I decided after only a few levels it simply wasn't worth it.", "I really like this game so far. However, I think it's a bit excessive to wait so long for the free gift box and the rotating purchasable cards. I also stopped encountering the Welsh Cookie Jar ads which makes many of the tasks impossible for me to complete in order to progress through to the next stage.", "The game is fun up until a certain point. After the first few levels I realized that there is constantly soo many things moving or blocking something I want to tap. The art style is cute but once you get over that it's gets boring quickly.", "As many other reviews have said. Other tycoon games with automatic manager cards do it much better. It's slow to make progress and is luck based whether you get manager cards to advance which only comes in a gift box that take hours to renew. You also need biscuits to upgrade which rarely appear. You'll spend more time watching ads for coins that barely impact anything and get stuck waiting for the gift box for a card than actually playing the game.", 'Game has too many ads, most are "optional" but it makes them in the way of gameplay and pretty necessary to progress at a reasonable pace. $25 to get rid of them is too high a cost. Don\'t install.', "I've spent more time watching non-mutable ads than actually playing the game. Also every 10 seconds a floating balloon takes up 1/3 of the playable screen and asks you to watch an ad for money. This game would be so cute and fun if it was playable", 'Fun until watching so many ads to get ahead gets to a point where you no longer can progress in the game fast enough. Stuck at day 8 with no way of getting more upgrades to move things along. Tired of watching ads and doing the same thing all hour...', 'The game has too many ads. If you play 15 minutes of the game 50% of it will be taken by ads. It\'s really not got alot of content. Sometimes you can voluntarily not watch the ads, but sometimes they sneek in the button that forces you to watch a "short ad". I hate how much advertising there is ok the game to make you spend money, along side the millions of ads you have to watch. It is not child friendly due to the amount of ads. The 5 star ratings feel fake and were bought.', "Just an app to watch ads. I don'tind ads in games but i spend more time watching ads in game then playing the game. Even when given the option to skip the ad and get less of a bonus it STILL plays the add. It's super annoying", 'Tutorial has no ads. After the tutorial the gameplay is literally unplayable because of ads popping up everywhere, floating across the screen and forcing you to watch to progress at all. I would give this game -1 star if I could', 'Im currently playing the game and it keeps sending me to the playstore to download an app, there was no ads everytime it did that, its making it difficult to play cause i have to exit the playstore and reenter the game. Fix this bug.', 'I really wanted to like this game but the amount of ads and the ad balloon flying over the tasks so you click on it instead of the task is too much. Gave it a try, do not recommend!', "It's a fine game. But you need to make sure to watch ads get bonus mission reward. If not, you need to throw in cash. Not very free2play game. The bone cookies are too less for each ads reward.", 'Too many adds! Could hardly play the game for adverts that kept on being shoved in front of the screen. Then they swap the buttons so you accidentally click the button to not get adverts only to end up with more adverts. Too many adverts for such a pretty game', 'The game is really cute and relaxing. But overall the "error" is really getting on my nerves & theres too many ads like its everywhere. But its still fun for me and cute, I recommend this game for relaxing and if your into cute games ☺️🐾', "Cute game but the art style of the ads and actual game do not match. Not what I came for. There's also no customization unlike what the game description insinuates, it's a conveyor belt assembly game. Ads will also autoplay even if you decline the giftbox so what's the point of letting me say no?,", "Balloon gets in the way when I'm trying to tap dogs that I can't automate yet, either have the balloon be an icon on the side like the biscuit jar or let me toggle the balloon on and off. I'd rather have random pop up ads than a balloon that gets in the way. Also let me sell extra manager cards for bones so I can afford to automate", "Day 2 for me and it's been good so far, keep in mind that this game is like those types that resets after you clear the day. It can be a painful to see all the stuff you collect (game time) gone after you accomplish one day", "The ads are a bit too much. I usually don't mind them, but there's a lot Also that stupid reward balloon constantly get sin the way and makes me miss things", 'Cute but way too many ads. It has ad based objectives and every time you start a new level the music turns back on.', "I like this game but the problem is why can't we just buy new servings? I thought it was gonna be like that other cooking cat game, but it is way different!", 'You need to watch a "short" ad at random times to complete the tasks you patiently waited for? I don\'t mind supporting developers via watching ads for things, but this was ridiculous. Cute concept for a game but no thank you.', "I love this game! Super cute 🍭 BUT, i don't like that there are diffrent days cause you loose gold and your progress. This can make me a bit frustrated, but overall a very good game!", 'Thier other games are much better as AFK production line games. This one progresses way to slow without purchasing in game content. Even with buying VIP, I still am progressing incredibly slowly. Compared to thier hamster and cat Cafe games, this one is not good.', 'The constant adds at the bottom making it impossible to click on things at the bottom of the screen is obnoxious and turned me completely off of the game.', "This game forces you to watch ads. And when you watch the optional ads that boost you, it's eventually not enough to keep progressing.", "The game is unbelieveably unbalanced. It costs 150 bones to buy a dog card but there aren't a lot of opportunities to get bones or even cards to get the dogs. You literally can't progress unless you come back every 4 hours to open a free gift just to get resources.", "Put a two as it showed 'error 403' message of me not being allowed to play?? Didnt even get to play very sad:( when fixed will chnage review, thank you if you saw and fixed the problem im sure its a great game and its just a problem that will be solved in no time 😊", "Way too many ads, I'd be fine with them most of the time but I keep getting 30 seconds ads with some even unskippable, gets way too annoying."]

title: Dog Game - The Dogs Collector!
description:
With cute art and adorable mini-games, you’ll be caring for your puppies in Dog Game any chance you get! Thousands have given Dog Game two furry paws up! 🐾

Dog Game is simple yet highly-addictive! To play, all you need to do is collect different kinds of cute & unique dogs and build a home for them, your very own Dog Tower! You can craft decoration and create lovely rooms to unlock cute new puppies to fill them with every single day.

Collect adorable dogs like shiba inu, husky, pug, bulldog, golden retriever and beagle! There’s over 900 puppys you can collect! 💫 Decorate rooms in your dog towers with your favourite styles: unicorn, fancy, legendary, anime, magic and so many more!


🌟 DOG GAME HIGHLIGHTS

● 900+ kawaii puppies to collect!
● Watch your animals come to life with cute animations
● Craft furniture and decorate your dream Dog Tower
● Play special events and earn exclusive pups & prizes
● Enter contests to design the most adorable rooms
● Play fun & addictive mini-games to earn coins
● Join a club & play with your friends (and make new ones)
● Compete in the leaderboard for exclusive rewards
● Daily missions & contests!
● There’s something new every week!


🏠 DECORATE YOUR OWN PUPPY TOWER

Create & personalize an adorable dog tower for all of your puppies to live in! Craft adorable decorations like plants, couches, dog toys, windows, sandcastles and adorable animal furniture.

You will adopt dogs of different themes and vibes according to your own taste! 70’s, beach, dance club, farm, underwater, or royalty. 


💖 PLAY GAMES WITH FRIENDS

Dog Game is a great pet game to play with friends! You can enter contests where you compete by designing the best dog room! You will play with dog lovers across the world! Dog Game is an amazing way to make new friends and socialize in new clubs!

Enter fun events throughout the year where you can earn unique rare dogs and special prizes! Unlock new challenging levels by playing minigames! 

Participate in non-stop dog-themed games like:
● BarckyBlocks: Match blocks like in tetris and beat all high scores
● PuppyPops: Match adorable dogs and earn lots of coins
● Spin the Basket
● And more!


✨ YOUR VIRTUAL PET AWAITS YOU IN DOG GAME

Your future pups are waiting for you now! Put your paws to work, play with friends & clubs, and get Dog Game today for free!
summary: Adopt 900+ Cute Puppies, Play Games, Craft Items & Decorate a Lovely Dog Tower

comments: ['Been playing this game for over a year and have really enjoyed it. Recently though, the events are just reskins of either floors from Cat Game or repeats of already past events. While a little repeat is to be expected, it just seems like they stopped caring about working on this game. Getting to the point where I am done with the regular tower and there are no options to continue, unless I spend actual money. Getting a little disappointed, because it is a fun game most times.', "This app won't work properly for me. I downloaded it, chose my starter dog, then it went to the house and the only thing it showed was the floor and the dog I chose. No tutorial. I thought it was just like that and I've played the cat game, so I fed her and even got two decos as well as the next dog. But I ran out of food and nothing. I couldn't do anything. So I closed the app and got back in and it restarted. From the beginning where you choose the dog.", "I've played dg for 2 yrs and cg for 1 yr. Lately cg has become unplayable due to lag. I worry the same will happen here after having invested thousands of hrs and $. Dog Game lacks some features from Cat Game & the crafting + leveling is overall more difficult. It lacks a full VIP reward system as well. My biggest issue is with player support. Often we feel ignored with our feedback & concerns. We know we won't get help from certain support staff. Bugs are left unfixed & there is no compensation", 'Really great game with awesome drawings. The one thing that I would complain about is the ads; right after you play a mini game,it just gives you a pop-up ad. I believe this is similar to the cat game, so if you are interested in the game, this game will surely spark your interest.', "Great game! I really love it and I enjoy it. I think it runs smoothy and it's really fun to collect dogs. I do have one thing that bothers me. Recently I've been having to uninstall and reinstall the game because it keeps glitching. Whenever I load the game up and I'm waiting in the loading screen once it gets to 100% the dog glitches out and then my screen goes black. Nothing happens after that and it's been happening recently. I hope this can get fixed. It's still a great game, love it!", "Cute and fun time waster about collecting dogs! I haven't been able to put it down! For such a simple concept it sure is fun. It's a bit money hungry but not overly so. A purchase removes ads, at least. They are generous with premium currency so that's always a plus. It would be nicer if there were more than 2 mini games to earn coins, though. Overall I'm happy with this game. The dogs are super cute, there are a ton of different ones (real and fantasy) and the wait times are not that bad!", "The cuteness can't be denied, and I love how every dog has their own unique animation - that makes the collecting all the more worthwhile! My main gripe is that advancing depends heavily on crafting, which takes a good amount of both resources and coins, which are hard to earn with only two mini games. There's a whole lot of waiting involved (wait for boxes to be delivered, wait for food options to be refreshed, wait for crafting to be completed) and the minigames are both pretty short plays.", "I really love the game but I've recently started having issues with booting the game up. It will load the start screen and once it starts loading, it give me a black screen and I can no longer play it. I've uninstalled and reinstalled it a couple of times and it loads my save, vut after a few times of playing, it give me the dreaded black screen again. Not sure who to contact because the black screen won't really allow me to contact anyone. 😕", "Recently it's just been glitching out at the loading screen and going black. I've been trying for a week or so now just to get loaded into the game, but it will instead freeze up and sometimes make me restart my phone entirely. It was fun for a bit, I guess, and I like it more than CG because I'm a dog person... but it is quite literally unplayable.", "This is my updated review! It took a few trys to actually get the game to the point where i had a game id and it would save my progress. The game is addicting but you have to be lucky with the spins in the beginning to actually be able to move on. Its not a problem after you get past the tutorial part but in the beginning if you keep getting dogs then you don't have enough supplies to continue and you have to start over. This needs to be fixed for future players! It is still a pretty fun game!", "its awsome! i love it so cute the one thing that bothers me is when you get a puppy it comes in a basket and when you get to a higher level it take soo long to get out of the basket but it isn't to big of a problem so i still give it five stars its a very fun game so i recomend it its very cute i play it so much", "I really love the game:) 1. No issues 2 . No laggy stuff 3. Not a lot of ads 4.Really fun and colorful 5.a lot of reskins from cat game but I don't mind", "After continuously getting the black screen when trying to load, I deleted the game then re-installed it. It worked! But now it's doing the same thing AGAIN. I'm missing another event because of these issues, and I did very much enjoy the game. This whole situation, however, is really souring my opinion and enjoyment, ESPECIALLY due to the developers' lack of action and response.", "I LUV it!!! It's SOOO cute and fun. I very rarely rate 5 starts so be proud of yourself! Very underrated! I don't even get pop up adds! 100% recomend! Update: I'm changing my rating. Its not letting me play anymore. Only thing I can do is click the play button. I can hear the music but after I click the play button it brings me to a black screen and nothing happens. Just the music playes. Pls fix.", "It's cute but it gets old doing the same two mini games over and over to earn coins. And sometimes when you watch an ad, it completely freezes the game (sometimes my phone too) and then crashes. Also the percentage of landing a dog the further you go is annoying. I want to continue to get more rooms, not collect an over amount of materials.", "the game doesn't work. it makes me restart the game every time and it doesn't show anything but the dogs. no tutorial or menu. nothing.", 'I love this game, from the art to the gameplay its highly addictive. I do suggest it to everyone, as a dog lover i love every piece of it! To the devs thank you so much for making it. Have a nice day', "This game is super fun to play casually when you need something to do. The mini games are super user friendly and super helpful when you need some coins. The crafting section is great, but my only complaint is that it takes a while to get a dog in any room, and my barbecue room has a huge amount of cotton before there's even a chance you can get a dog. Other than that, not disappointed!☺️", "The game is cute. Its just as fun as cat collector, which I've played for almost 3 years now. But this one has too any ads! After each round of game play there is an ad before you get your coins. Ger rid of that please! There is a glitch in the doggopedia, I can't see most of my dogs, and when I scroll through it, it doesn't work correctly. Each time I deliver a basket or feed for supplies, instead of going back where I was, I'm taken to the top of the tower. It's just frustrating.", "Crafting recipes are so difficult. Would definitely like to see them be changed to be like Cat Game's recipes. An option to permanently opt out of global chat (CG got this recently) would be amazing. I think the % chance of getting a dog is a lie, feels like I have to wait and spin so many times before I get one. I love this game, I'm enjoying it even more than CG (that I've played for 2+ years and am almost max level on). With a few tweaks, I think it'll be perfect!", "This game has been a lot of fun so far. The dogs are super cute and my 4yr old daughter absolutely loves them all. Problem now is that the game was asking me to update, but it hasn't 😕 had the spinning circle the entire day. Tried resetting my phone, nothing. Tried turning it off then back on, nothing. I even tried Uninstalling to see if that would work but now it won't even let me re-install! 🥺 Please help fix this bug!", "This game is sooo cute!! I definitely recommend it. It does have very few ads, but it can take a really long time to get a basket. Otherwise, It's very fun!", "Amazing game! I love the designs and animations, foods are cute. I love every dog and I'm attached to all of them! I just hate the fact that you have to wait for a very very long time because then I either have to do random stuff for the long time on the game or just leave and go back later which annoys me a bit. Good game overall though", 'i loved cat game so much even though i\'m a dog person so obviously i\'m super into dog game! it really is the best. (1.) it\'s calming without being boring. (2.) you never run out of things to do, but there\'s no stressful feeling of like "ugh it\'s too much work." (3.) there\'s mini games! and the adorable dog home decor challenges? ugh yes, so fun! (4.) the mini games are actually fun and you get coins for playing them. i\'d love a unicorn version in the future!', "Very cute game. I love this game and CG, but I play this more since I'm more of a dog person than a cat person. The only real issue I have with it is that sometimes the loading gets stuck at around 55%, and I have to restart the app to get back to the home screen. The premium keys aren't very easy to get as the only way is through completing floors, and it would be great if you could add the ability to add friends and private messages!", "Recently been having issues with the game loading, I get a blank screen with music playing. I've tried on two separate phones and tried re-downloading it. When it does finally load it works for a few minutes and then crashes. Seems to be an issue for a lot of people right now, so hoping it can be fixed soon.", "I really liked it to start. Got all the way to level 23 and suddenly got stuck on a black screen. I uninstalled and reinstalled and had to start all over. Support says they can't help me because the game added random numbers to the end of my screenname and I don't know them. Started all over and now it's stuck on the black screen again when I try to open it. I think I'm done.", "I enjoy this game a lot, super cute and fun to play, I love the different themes :) Edit: As I level up, the chances are becoming too low, and collecting is difficult. I'm only level 15 - hope to see some tweaks in this area as the game has so much potential!", "It's basically the cat game, but with dogs! I've loved the cat game since my friend introduced me to it a few years ago, and when my sibling brought this to my attention I couldn't pass up the opportunity to play. Aside from minor stylistic changes it's the same; so it's perfect to play when I'm waiting on things to craft in the cat game (and vice versa) While it seems a little odd to have the same themes as paid for floors in the cat game be free in this one, that's really the only flaw imo", "Very annoying. After waiting for a few months for it to catch onto some of CG's better qualities and not just compile its worst the game only presented a black screen every time I attempted to log into it. For two days, everytime I tried to get into the heart of the app this happened. Since I know the first thing is always suggested to Uninstaller and reinstall, I did that and the game started me over and says backup and restoring can't be done. What a waste.", 'Definitely a super fun game. Crafting is a little harder than Cat Game but still really fun. Great support too. They just restored both of my accounts after having to get a new phone and not being able to get back into my old Google Play account. The only thing I wish they would allow is for us to be able to gift more than 10 items at a time to club members requesting items.', "Was looking for a cute collection game with a very specific want for a clean colorful style, and this + cat game fits the bill very well. I like to support games I'm fond of so I've allowed myself to purchase ONE floor from each, and otherwise haven't felt compelled to purchase anything at all to proceed. I do wish there were more mini games I admit, a simple endless runner I believe would go over really well, but all in all a lot of fun, can't complain!", "I wrote this review on the cat alternative so I figured I'd mention it here too. It's an amazing game but there are some wifi troubles. It could just be me but for both games I have to frequently switch my wifi on and off because you need wifi to play but the game won't load when it's on. Sometimes you need wifi to do things and sometimes you can play offline perfectly fine which is weird. Other than that it's sooo adorable and I highly recommend it!!", "Also having the black screen after the loading as others are reporting. A little disappointed that it's right in the middle of an event and more disappointed now that I may get auto-booted from my club before this gets fixed. I'm really trying to hang in there because I enjoy Cat Game so much, but it's getting very difficult.", "An inferior version of Cat Game, which is a shame cause I really love the cute dogs as well. Crafting is such a nightmare though - both regular and events. It's not nearly as much of a slog to get through levels twice as high up as the ones in my little dog tower. Feels like they want you to spend money to move faster but nah. I'd get more for my money from their own other product.", "Changed my rating. We had to get to like the 4th floor before we were able to quit the game and have it save. My son and I both downloaded this. Played it a bunch. I got to the second level with 2 dogs when I stopped playing. Next time I went into the game, all my progress was gone except the original dog that I picked. The same thing happened with my son. I love the cat game and had high hopes for this one. If you fix the bug, I'll gladly change my rating.", "Hi! I've been playing dog game for a few months now, but suddenly the app started closing on me and now after the loading screen it goes dark and won't open the game. I've Uninstalled it and reinstalled it, it connected to my account, and again the same problem. I'd contact support, but if I can't open the app I'm not sure how to contact support. Any idea why this is happening or how I can fix it? Thanks in advanced!", "Ever since the update I can't play the game. I LOVED playing it. The update has caused the game to no load. The start screen comes up, press the start button, says its loading to 55% then it just goes black and nothing else happens. I'm super upset because I love playing the game but now I'm also missing out on the events that are going on. Really hoping this gets fixed fast.", 'I play "Cat Game" as well this game is just as cute and is easy to play, however it\'s not as convenient as "Cat Game". I don\'t like the way hearts cannot be collected in one tap and expire too quickly. It takes up too much space on the club screen and messes with our club\'s ability to chat.', "900 dogs and no Index to keep track! ...... I started to play the game and it seemed okay .... Then, upon getting my first 'epic' dog I went to look for it but couldn't find it. I then realized that ALL dogs appear as the same level once opened. I searched for some type of index to differentiate the dogs but nothing. I informed the support team and they said there was no such option in the game. Absolute fail."]

title: Date in Australia: Chat & Meet
description:
Looking for love or making friends with people in the Australian region? Aussie Social is the app for you!

Dating is easy with Aussie Social. Whether you are looking for a friend to hang out with, finding your soulmate, or meet attractive single men or women in Australia or New Zealand. With the simple touch of your mobile phone, Aussie Social gives you the easiest way to communicate, chat and interact with awesome people in Down Under!

Our mission is to help you find the type of relationship you are looking for.

What makes Aussie Social unique is this: You can meet people directly by watching videos of them. Meeting new people, making friends, chatting, socializing, and even dating has never been that fun!

Unlike other networks… we have video profiles! They say a picture is worth a thousand words and a video is at least a thousand pictures! We created a video based social app because you can express yourself more accurately with videos and let your personality shine through! Too shy to upload a video? We have photos too but the videos are much more exciting! 

Don't feel like looking at photos or videos of people and singles? Then hangout in our chat rooms and message people nearby or everywhere else right away. Chat with local people or join the world chat room and chat with people from all over the world.

Love to meet new people, make friends or find a date to hangout with tonight? It's easy! You can start by seeing video clips of singles and when you like someone, just click the heart. If they like you back, we will connect both of you. Want to help break the ice? Send them a ‘Hi’! You can send unlimited messages, videos and photos to each other. Finding a date, meeting new friends, chatting, dating has never been so easy. And best of all, it's FREE! 

Our Features?
- group social chat rooms
- private inbox with photo, video and audio
- make fans (people that like you)
- or friends (people you like back)
- video and photo profiles
- tags system in profiles
- FREE way to meet new friends
summary: Online Social Networking app to Connect with Australian people from Down Under

The whole thing is just a silly joke. Bollocks you're trying to make this site legitimate. I just pick 2 different photos and began scroll through. They both regularly reappear with different names and different Australian towns. Totally bogus!", "Couldn't change location which was detected correctly, but settings advised it wasn't accurate. Requested profiles within 50km then shown accounts from other states, one photo 3 times each from different states, one after another. Account deleted within 20 minutes. Don't waste your time", 'THIS APPLICATION IS A DISGUSTING DISASTER, AND AND IT IS BLOCKING ME FROM DELETING IT. GOOGLE SHOULD REMOVE IT AND REMOVE THE DEVELOPER. IT IS IMPOSSIBLE TO USE WITHOUT CONSTANT BLOCKING FROM DISGUSTING ADVERTS. THIS FEEDBACK, IS MY BELIEF ONLY WITHOUT PREJUDICE. THE FILTERS DO NOT WORK, AND I AM GETTING CONTACTS FROM OVERSEAS WHEN I SAID AUSTRALIA ONLY. DEVELOPER UNHELPFULL.', "Please fix your filtering festure, this is the 4th time I've requested this. what is the point of clicking the funnel icon to set the distance filter, to 50Km, for example, yet the entire of Asia still shows up. Asia is not 50Km from Brisbane, Queensland, Australia. Also.. you are not giving a care in the world who signs up and pays - for as long as they pay, that's all; you care about. Regardless if their profile is fake. Listen... 99.99999% of people who live in the UK. Don't want fake or", 'It is good app i found some good but there are some using fake profile when i call its way different look than their profile pic..and when you chat its always pause due to oncoming notifications..thats they only isuue..but its a good app hope i could find my forever here😊', "Terrible app, it is rife with bot accounts despite their purported verification process, some of the fake accounts are blatantly obvious (there are many 'females' on the app with male names, for example). title: Dog whistle & training app
description:
EveryDoggy: all-in-one puppy & dog training app, created by certified canine experts. Built-in clicker for training sessions, fun tricks, essential commands, ultimate puppy FAQs and many more! All you need to socialize, train and make friends with your dog is now on one app.

You can train your dog using our built-in whistle.
Dog whistles emit a high frequency sound which is inaudible to humans but is loud for dogs. 
Dog whistle generates frequencies ranging from 22,000 Hz to 25,000 Hz.

Are you afraid that your lovely pet will chew on your favorite shoes or make your new carpet their toilet? With EveryDoggy you’ll learn how to end and prevent any unwanted behaviors.

EveryDoggy's philosophy is based on three important Ps.
We are:
* Personalized. You'll discover a video training program that meets the goals you have for your pooch.
* Professional. Our certified pro-experts with many years of experience know how to teach every doggy.
* Practical. No excessive training theory, just practice… a lot of practice!

What exactly does EveryDoggy have for you?

* Personalized Puppy & Adult dog training sessions
Do you want to help your pup to take his first steps at home or teach your dog some impressive tricks? Our step-by-step video courses will meet your needs exactly!

* Problem-solving guides
Having to deal with problems can really make you feel paralyzed and desperate. But don’t worry, we’ve got your back! EveryDoggy provides effective solutions to behavioral problems. Learn to address leash pulling, house soiling, chewing, excessive barking, separation anxiety, unwanted jumping up, and more.

* Built-in clicker
A clicker is a great tool that can make positive reinforcement training more efficient. While training, use the clicker exactly when your dog performs the desired behavior and therefore, reinforce this behavior. You don’t have to purchase a clicker or a whistle as EveryDoggy already has these as built-in features.

* Positive reinforcement methods only
You love your dog. So do we! We use only positive reinforcement methods to make training fun and simple.

* Certified professional experts
All our content is created by certified dog trainers dedicated to your success.

Start training with EveryDoggy and live a happy life with your obedient and well-mannered pet!
summary: Puppy training app with dog clicker and whistle to raise an obedient pet
